INSERT INTO `articles_article` VALUES (1,'The secrets of pro players: use these 6 simple tricks to win almost all your battle royale games','the-secrets-of-pro-players-use-these-6-simple-tricks-to-win-almost-all-your-battle-royale-games-1228','<p>Hello survivor, to prevail in any battle royal game you need tactics and skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It more than just a game of killing every opponent you come across especially when you are playing squad mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://res.feednews.com/assets/v2/6ad15365ab27744c648c7ce2fb3e3cfa?quality=uhq&amp;resize=720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A battle royale game consists of a large number of players ranging from 50 upward in an island. The major aim of the game is to survive and be the last man/team standing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examples of popular battle royale games are Call of Duty mobile, Garena Free Fire, Player Unknown Battleground (PUBG), Fortnite etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://res.feednews.com/assets/v2/3c522abe50421615a3faf527210f6b29?quality=uhq&amp;resize=720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The skills a gamer must possess are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. <strong>Confidence.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes! , confidence is a skill. Not all gamers possess this. You will notice some players heart beating at the rate of 100 beats per min just because they encountered a player who seems like a pro to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://res.feednews.com/assets/v2/27891bd717d113c7b54f3fd396f89545?quality=uhq&amp;resize=720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>How do you improve your gaming confidence?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trust me, to do this you will not care about your point, rank or anything. This is going to take you about a week to master. First, jump into a crowded area and try to survive. The Center of the map is always crowded, jump there. Second, don&#39;t depend on a favourite gun. Pick any and fight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. <strong>Speed.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must be a fast thinker to kick your opponent to the lobby. One way to do this is practice solo vs squad. This will train your fingers to swipe fast and think fast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. <strong>Tactics.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note that playing solo is quite different from squads. Squad mode requires more tactics. For example, don&#39;t land at the end of the map, in games like free fire it&#39;s usually crowded. This seems to work in other games but not free fire. It&#39;s safe to move with the safe zone when playing solo, but in squad mode, it&#39;s better to be in the safe zone before it starts collapsing. Don&#39;t move along with it, because all other teams will start moving this time. That&#39;s a hell of war. So once you get the notice that the safe zone will soon start to collapse, you and your teammates should quickly move to the next safe zone</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://res.feednews.com/assets/v2/831c0f9cc88de3d0c71322d511597e0b?quality=uhq&amp;resize=720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. <strong>Reviving Teammates.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s a bad practice to revive your teammates when you&#39;ve not eliminated the enemy. Some players are funny that they will start reviving their teammates while taking damage from opponents. That&#39;s bad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. <strong>Learn Headshot</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One thing pros master is how to take out their enemy with few shots. You can achieve this through practice. Practice with AIs and real player. Aim for the head only. Increase your sensitivity and drag your fire button up when shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://res.feednews.com/assets/v2/aec5c1c56693d654142a5715bfa2024e?quality=uhq&amp;resize=720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. <strong>Don&#39;t be stagnant.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the reason PC players have more edge than mobile gamers. PC players can move and shoot the same time, this is why they are difficult to target. As a mobile gamer, do not stay in a spot for long. When shooting, continue to drag your movement joystick as this makes it harder for the opponent to target you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The key point to always remember when playing a battle royale game Is that every player can be killed. Your confidence matters a lot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you play free fire?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a tip from a pro player on how to push your rank easily.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"youtube-embed-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;padding-top:30px;height:0;overflow:hidden\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tBw9TbfjWO8\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','freefire cod pubg battleroyale','pics/Screenshot_20201208-223114.png','2020-12-08 21:43:30.371149','2020-12-08 21:43:30.371205','2020-12-14 08:58:16.574415','published',2,12,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guidlines',0,0),(13,'Pro tips to counter the new Vector gun on free fire','pro-tips-to-counter-the-new-vector-gun-on-free-fire','<p>Hello survivor, why complain about the new Vector gun when there is a proven way to punish any opponent holding it?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ever since the introduction of Vector, I&#39;ve seen countless free fire gamers complain about its insane fire rate. As if that&#39;s not enough, players can also equip two of the weapon at once.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Free fire vector akimbo\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2020/12/10/ff2.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This gives it the power of the Poker Mp40 which would have been&nbsp;the best gun skin to counter the weapon. Sadly, mp40&nbsp;has been removed from the clash squad weapon list.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"vector vs poker\" height=\"326\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2020/12/10/ff.jpg\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not fret when your opponents equip the gun, you can try any of the tips below to take down the opponent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. A Shot Gun and at least one gloo wall.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A shotgun does high damages with few shots. It&#39;s a weapon to silence the opponent without wasting much time. You should note that you don&#39;t engage any opponent holding the vector gun in a rapid-fire gun fight because they will surely overpower you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"gloo wall image\" height=\"390\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2020/12/10/ffr.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therefore, after every two-shot place a gloo wall to defend. If you are using an M1014, be sure you don&#39;t equip a gun skin with a low fire rate. Also, M1014 has high recoil, you should place a wall after every two-shot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Do not engage in a rapid-fire gunfight.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just to buttress the first point, ensure you don&#39;t engage in a rapid-fire gunfight with any player holding the beast. Instead, stay behind a cover or place a gloo wall after shooting for some seconds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.Taking them from afar.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The gun has a fair range, it becomes&nbsp;less powerful and accurate as the distance increases. Therefore, you should try to bait them into a long-range fight. An assault rifle would be the best weapon to equip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. If you can&#39;t beat &#39;em, join &#39;em!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"fighting with vector aakimbo gun\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2020/12/10/ff3.jpg\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We cannot shy away from the fact that the vector gun is one of the best weapons to equip in clash squad mode. If you are finding it hard to knock down players using the gun, then you should buy the weapon in the next round. Do not join those who say &quot;Vector is for noobs&quot;, a pro prayer utilise resources around for his benefits. Therefore, the best way to knock down Vector users is to use Vector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch the video of Vector gun in action.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zmku3tHLMJU\" width=\"640\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Was this tip helpful?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Click the like button at the bottom of the page and share with your friends also.</p>','freefire proplayer','pics/ff2.png','2020-12-10 13:37:29.674152','2020-12-10 13:37:29.674199','2021-03-07 12:24:49.976035','published',2,12,1,1,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guidlines',0,1),(14,'After HTML and CSS What\'s Next? | Roadmap To Web Development In 2021','after-html-and-css-whats-next-roadmap-to-web-development-in-2021','<p>I could remember vividly that I spent 6 months perambulating in 2016, from HTML to C++ just to get my hands on web development. The learning curve wasn&#39;t easy because I made a lot of mistakes while trying to get started with&nbsp;web development. I studied if not all free courses available on Sololearn before I decided to make research on the actual language I needed for web development. This article aims to enlighten anyone who wants to be a web developer in 2021&nbsp;on the steps to take to avoid the mistake I made in 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>After HTML and CSS What&#39;s Next?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>I would say decision making comes next. It high time you decide on which end of web development you want to stay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Decision making at a junction \" height=\"403\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2021/01/09/screenshot_20210109-184715.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although, sitting on the fence is allowed. When I say &quot;which end&quot;, I mean&nbsp;you are to choose whether you are going <strong><a href=\"https://www.moremehub.com/15/this-is-how-i-would-explain-the-front-end-back-end-and-apis-to-a-four-year-old-child/\">Frontend</a> </strong>or <strong><a href=\"https://www.moremehub.com/15/this-is-how-i-would-explain-the-front-end-back-end-and-apis-to-a-four-year-old-child/\" target=\"_blank\">Backend</a>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are finding it hard to decipher the meaning of Frontend and backend, I wrote an article about those terms. In the article, I explained the terms frontend, backend and API in such a way a four-year-old would understand. You might want to <a href=\"https://www.moremehub.com/15/this-is-how-i-would-explain-the-front-end-back-end-and-apis-to-a-four-year-old-child/\" target=\"_blank\">check it out</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While you are learning HTML and CSS, I assume you have an insight into the &#39;end&#39; which suits you. Do you enjoy coding&nbsp;beautiful web pages or you prefer writing the logic behind those pretty pages? Whichever you choose would determine the &#39;end&#39; that suits you. If you love the former, you should choose the frontend learning path, later? then stick to the backend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Learn JavaScript</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What do facebook.com, twitter.com, youtube.com&nbsp;and other prominent&nbsp;websites have in common?&nbsp;its JavaScript!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Learn JavaScript First\" height=\"292\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2021/01/09/screenshot_20210109-184909.png\" width=\"637\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Irrespective of the &#39;end&#39;&nbsp;you choose, I would recommend you learn JavaScript. JavaScript is an essential programing language for adding dynamic features to your website. Javascript is powerful to run at the frontend (Vue, React, Angular) and the backend(Node.js).&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://sololearn.com\" target=\"_blank\">Sololearn</a> and <a href=\"http://w3schools.com\">W3CSS</a> have great beginner-friendly tutorials to get you on track.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do you&nbsp;prefer the front End?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should get your thumbs busy&nbsp;with any of the frontend frameworks. Having a profound knowledge of the&nbsp;underlying technology stack of these frameworks is a prerequisite(JavaScript). Examples of front end frameworks are Vue, React and Angular.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do you prefer the Back End?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backend frameworks&nbsp;are built&nbsp;on different programming languages. To stay on track, you must have a good knowledge of the underlying technology of the framework. There are lots of backend frameworks which includes Django, Laravel, Node, Ruby On Rail. Django uses Python, Laravel uses PHP, Node uses JS and Rail uses Ruby programming language. Whichever you use, its important to understand the prerequisites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Version Control</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also known as <strong>Source Control, </strong>is a practice of monitoring and managing the changes that happen to source codes. I would recommend Git for tracking and managing your source codes once you get started with the framework of your choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Learn version control like Git\" height=\"613\" src=\"/media/post_images/admin/2021/01/09/screenshot_20210109-185253.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can learn git commands on Sololearn, they have a comprehensive and beginner-friendly tutorial on it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, if you stick to my channel on MoremeHub, I promise to guide you on the right path on Web development. Hit the follow button at the bottom of the page.</p>','webdevelopment ,html ,css,javascript, django, laravel, php','pics/FB_IMG_1610041056765.jpg','2021-01-09 17:40:44.432878','2021-01-09 17:40:44.432918','2021-03-06 16:42:02.454106','published',253,1,1,1,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guidlines',0,1),(15,'This is how I would explain the front-end, back-end, and APIS to a four-year-old child','this-is-how-i-would-explain-the-front-end-back-end-and-apis-to-a-four-year-old-child','<p>Recently, I told a friend of mine that I am a back-end developer. He asked me what the meaning of &ldquo;back-end&rdquo; web development was. It took me lots of explanation and illustration to explain what back-end means in web development. I understand, he is not a techy guy. I noticed that not just non-techy are finding it hard to understand the terms, a lot of coding newbies can&rsquo;t decipher the meaning. While some who think they &ldquo;understand&rdquo; probably <strong>misunderstood</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just like I explained to my friend, this article is aimed at explaining various aspects (&ldquo;ends&rdquo;) of web development to newbies as I would explain to a 4-year-old. Don&rsquo;t be offended when I say <strong>&lsquo;like a four-year-old&rsquo;</strong>, the phrase is to tell how simple and explicit the explanation would be.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would represent the world of web development with a medium-sized restaurant. In a restaurant, you enter and give your order, &nbsp;the waiter brings the&nbsp;order to your table.<br />\r\nBasically, you are the user of the restaurant(website). You are less concerned with the processes of making the food. You just want your food and make payment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Front-end Aspect Of The Restaurant.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The front end is everything you can see in the restaurant. The HTML is synonymous with the structure of the restaurant, the tables, chairs, and other things. The <strong>CSS</strong> is the arrangement of things, the restaurant&rsquo;s painting, the styles and every other thing put in place. The <strong>JavaScript</strong> handles how you are attended to. When you walk into the restaurant, the waiter gives you the menu, you check your favourite and make a request.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"A medium restaurant\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/12/20210212_223128_0000.png\" /> Then the waiter knows what to do with your request. The waiter can also help you with other things in the restaurant.<br />\r\nTherefore, everything happening right there is the front-end aspect of the restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Back-end Aspect Of The Restaurants.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>After making your request, you are less concerned with the cook or the ingredients the restaurant&rsquo;s cook is using. You are there enjoying the serene environment and expecting the waiter to deliver your food.<br />\r\nYou can think of the back-end as the cooks working tirelessly to prepare the food you ordered. The waiter hands over the menu, then the cook prepares the food and give it to the waiter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cooks working in a restaurant\" height=\"1240\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/12/20210212_223421_0000.png\" width=\"1747\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can think of everything happening in the kitchen as the back-end. The management of the restaurant, which includes decisions on pricing, payment of staff salaries, is done behind. <strong>This is the back-end!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The APIs Aspect Of The Restaurant.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"A smiling waiter\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/12/20210212_223720_0000.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can think of the APIs as the waiters. They serve as a medium between the user and the cook/management.<br />\r\nJust like the way mini restaurants can do without waiters (case of a user requesting the cooks directly), websites can also do without APIs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"a small restaurant\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/12/20210212_223959_0000.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The API makes it possible to communicate with other mediums.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, if you own a blog app, you can get data across to a mobile app via the API.<br />\r\nAPIs also makes it possible to deliver foods outside the restaurant. You can think of the delivery men as the APIS.</p>','webdevelopment front-end back-end api','pics/20210212_222412_0000.png','2021-02-12 20:58:30.635259','2021-02-12 20:58:30.635294','2021-02-21 18:24:12.561573','published',253,1,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(19,'Reasons You Should Space Your Children In Marriage','reasons-you-should-space-your-children-in-marriage','<p>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"Degejednsb\" />Marriage is a blissful union of two people driven by passion and love for each order, but most people tend to forget what happens after marriage? The answer in our minds should probably be that they are to bear children. But why bear children that are not evenly spaced? Let&#39;s say you have three children and the first child&nbsp;is 15 years old, the second&nbsp;is 14 years old and the third&nbsp;is 13 years old, meaning that they are just one year older than each other.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Face\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This article is aimed at educating you on some of the importance of spacing your children in marriage.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spacing involves giving a little gap or space as it implies before giving birth to another child, let&#39;s say your first child&nbsp;is 18 years old, the second should be 15 years old, this is an ideal method of spacing and this has a lot of benefit to the family entirely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Father playing with children\" height=\"1240\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/21/20210221_181854_0000.png\" width=\"1747\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spacing allows you to save more for the family, taking care of infants can be expensive so if you after giving birth, decide with your spouse to wait a little longer before having the second child, you would be able to recover all expenses made on your child before giving birth to another.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"Sheejeb\" />Also, the human body grows weaker after every conception, this is because of the amount of blood a woman loses when delivering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Women during childbirth\" height=\"1240\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/02/21/20210221_182024_0000.png\" width=\"1747\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therefore,&nbsp;the woman needs to rest for about two years before taking in again, at least by this period she should have been able to regain the blood she lost during her first conception. This is one of the reasons why women age faster than men, they lose a lot&nbsp;of blood during childbirth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If they constantly lose this amount of blood, they will be looking 80 in their&nbsp;40s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, sex control is a very vital factor, learn to control and tame your body, despite the fact that it is your right to get intimate with your spouse, you should also learn to habit of self-control to achieve the best for your family.</p>','children marriage parenting','pics/20210221_181433_0000.png','2021-02-17 20:19:17.603512','2021-02-17 20:19:17.603573','2021-02-21 17:25:28.003627','published',651,18,1,1,'unlimited','Spelling/Grammatical errors in the body. Revise and resubmit',0,1),(22,'Moremehub Guildlines/Instructions for Content Creators','moremehub-guildlinesinstructions-for-content-creators','<p>It&nbsp;is important to take note of the following instructions/guidelines before you&nbsp;write your first article on moremehub to avoid rejections.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is the minimum number of words required per article?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your article must contain at least 300 words and a picture. However, on moremehub, quality of articles is determined by the text&nbsp;and not images added to the articles. Therefore, write more and use images and videos when&nbsp;necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Which type of articles are allowed on Moremehub?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please note that Moreme Hub is NOT a news website. Therefore, any news related articles will NOT be approved. Also, gists, gossips, and time-dependent articles are not allowed on moremehub.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examples of time-dependent articles: &quot;President Muhammadu Buhari gives new directives on covid 19 guidelines&quot;. You can write on personal development, what you love doing, howto/guides, opinion, politics etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guidelines On Images To Be Used.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We do not encourage random images downloaded from google,&nbsp;others artwork or copyrighted images. Please make use of stock photos for illustration. You can get your images from Canva. Better still, you can create your own images. This is why we encourage lesser images and more text to relieve writers of the stress of finding the right images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also note that disgusting, nude or pornography images are not allowed. It may get your account <strong>BANNED</strong> and all earnings FORFEITED.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Other Publishing Guidelines.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Partially or wholly Plagiarized articles are not allowed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Do not rewrite articles already existing on the hub.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Avoid Spelling/Grammatical&nbsp;errors in the body or title of your article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Do not write articles on money-making.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Adverts are not allowed&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Junk paragraphs or sentences are not allowed (e.g &quot;welcome to my channel&quot;)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Do not write articles about Moreme Hub (e.g &quot; how to publish an article on moremehub), leave that for the editors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For enquiries on payment, check the monetization tab on your dashboard.</strong></p>','moremehub','pics/20210217_220924_0000.png','2021-02-17 21:03:37.484871','2021-02-17 21:03:37.484940','2021-02-17 21:21:43.519656','published',1,11,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(25,'Signs And Symptoms Of Lung Cancer You Need To Pay Attention To','signs-and-symptoms-of-lung-cancer-you-need-to-pay-attention-to','<p>Lung cancer is a type of cancer that begins in the lungs. The lung is the organ in the body with the principal function of breathing, situated in the chest, it takes in oxygen after inhalation and releases carbon dioxide after exhaling.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lung cancer,&nbsp;also known as lung carcinoma, begins when the cells in the lungs grow rapidly, uncontrollably and abnormally in the tissues of the lung and forms a malignant tumour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The signs and symptoms of lung cancer don&#39;t appear most likely until the cancer is advanced. However, the list below entails some signs and symptoms you should notice as it could signify that you have lung cancer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>a.</strong> <strong>Coughing -&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Having a persistent cough is a symptom of lung cancer. People with lung cancer mostly experience a chronic cough that lasts for a long period of time. This frequent cough may be dry, with phlegm and could often time come with strains of blood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>b.</strong> <strong>Chest pain -&nbsp;</strong>One of the common symptoms of lung cancer is having tremendous chest pain, the pain could also appear in the ribs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>c.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Respiratory infections and shortness of breath </strong>-&nbsp;People with lung cancer often experience different respiratory infections, difficulties with breathing and breath shortness, as such, they have to gasp for breath more frequently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>d.</strong> <strong>Fatigue and loss of appetite -&nbsp;</strong>People with lung cancer often experience unnecessary fatigue. This fatigue is cancer-related, as no matter how much rest such a person takes, he/she would end up feeling tired and weak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>e. Frequent pain, especially in the bone and joint and repeated headache.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>f. Having swollen lymph nodes and weight loss is a symptom of lung cancer.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should however note that lung cancer cannot be self-diagnosed at home. It strictly requires a medical diagnosis. Even if you notice the signs and symptoms of lung cancer, you should, on no accord conclude that you have cancer until it is confirmed and affirmed by a standard medical practitioner. As such, you need to visit the hospital for a medical check-up regularly.</p>','cancer lung pain','pics/images_-_2021-02-16T093542.412.jpeg','2021-02-17 23:14:12.856256','2021-02-17 23:14:12.856301','2021-02-18 01:03:38.919654','published',657,27,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(29,'Make Your Delicious African Salad(ABACHA) Using These Simple Methods','make-your-delicious-african-saladabacha-using-these-simple-methods','<p>Abacha which is also known as African salad is a popular delicacy savoured by the inhabitants of Eastern Nigeria. It can be prepared using two methods which would be extensively explained.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ingredients required for the preparation of the African salad include the dry Abacha also known as tapioca, red oil, potash, pepper, salt, garden eggs, vegetables, crayfish, seasoning cubes, Ukpaka, onions, fresh fish.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Procedure for preparation.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 1:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In a clean bowl, add the tapioca and have it dissolved in cold water. This is to prevent the tapioca from getting too soft. Chop the onions and set them aside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wash the fresh fish and spice it with seasoning cubes and salt. Add some of the chopped onions and cook until tender.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add some oil to a pan, add the potash and mix well with the oil. Add the Ukpaka and continue the mixing. Add the seasoning cubes, crayfish and salt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add the tapioca which has already been transferred to a sieve to remove the excess water. Stir properly and set aside. Heat some oil and fry the fish until golden brown.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chop the vegetables, some onions, vegetables and fish. The African salad is ready.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 2:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Alternatively, you can decide to heat the oil. Add some chopped onions, crayfish, seasoning cubes, salt and allow the onions to fry a little.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remove from the heat and allow to cool. Add the already prepared Abacha to the oil and mix. In a separate bowl, add some oil and potash, then mix well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add the Ukpaka to the bowl, some salt and mix well. Chop an extra plate of onions, garden eggs, vegetables and set aside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transfer the well-mixed Abacha to a plate and garnish as desired. The African salad is ready and can be consumed with any drink of your choice.</p>','#food #abacha','pics/IMG_20210218_124915.jpg','2021-02-18 12:11:14.047942','2021-02-18 12:11:14.048004','2021-02-21 18:04:36.170122','published',669,28,1,0,'unlimited','Please add least one image to the body. Also, work on paragraphs',0,1),(39,'Meet 4 Nigerian Celebrities Who Care And Show Love To The Poor.','meet-4-nigerian-celebrities-who-care-and-show-love-to-the-poor','<p>In Nigeria, we have a lot of&nbsp;rich celebrities, some give to the poor and some don&#39;t, they only flaunt their riches on social media.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this article, I will show you four Nigerian stars and celebrities who have taken a bold step by giving what they have to the poor, homeless, and vulnerable, and I hope this will inspire you to give and show love to people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Williams Uchemba</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/02/19/screenshot_20210219-1624222_99FCQvB.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This actor is a very popular and wealthy one, he is also an Instagram comedian, a Nigerian actor, and philanthropist who has been in the Nollywood industry for over a decade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He has his own charity organization which specializes in giving to the less privileged. He disclosed that he has faced many spiritual attacks since he and his team started the act of giving. However, this has not stopped him from impacting the lives of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Tonto Dike</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"622\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/02/19/screenshot_20210219-1622002.png\" width=\"639\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tonto Dike is a Nigerian veteran actress who has been acting in movies for over 10 years now. She provides and gives food to various children in Nigeria.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tonto Dike is a very beautiful actress who is a close friend to a popular cross-dresser known as Bobrisky. Learn how to be a cheerful giver like her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Chika Ike.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"445\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/02/19/screenshot_20210219-1622232.png\" width=\"641\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chika Ike is a popular and beautiful Nigerian actress who gives to the less privileged and vulnerable. As you can see in the image above, she bought gifts for kids in Asaba, Delta state.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Regina Daniels</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"414\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/02/19/screenshot_20210219-1623042.png\" width=\"646\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regina Daniels is a young Nigerian actress and brand ambassador who is married to a billionaire known as Ned Nwoko, he is a politician, philanthropist, and lawyer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regina Daniels usually shows love to kids and provides them with gifts and other groceries. She also gives scholarships to students. She is indeed a cheerful giver and you should be like her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I urge you to give and show love to people no matter how little you have or earn.</p>','reginadaniels tontodikeh williamuchemba','pics/Screenshot_20210219-1623042.png','2021-02-19 17:05:48.319684','2021-02-19 17:05:48.320048','2021-02-20 11:34:28.188305','published',650,2,1,0,'unlimited','Your article was partially or wholly copied from another platform',0,1),(43,'\"Her Parents Are Aware Of Our Relationship\"-38 Years Old Man Who Gave A 17 Years Old Girl A Gun Claims','her-parents-are-aware-of-our-relationship-38-years-old-man-who-gave-a-17-years-old-girl-a-gun-claims','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"Fhsdsgehsgeheg\" style=\"float:left\" />Late last week news broke out that a 17 years old girl was caught with a gun in her school which she brought to shoot the teacher&nbsp;that told her to remove the dye she put on her hair, this incident happened in Calabar, Cross River.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ever since then, speculations on&nbsp;how she came in contact or gained access to a gun at such tender age and many more questions have been arising. The recent news which is even more surprising than the first is that the young 17 years old girl has admitted to being a member of a secret cult group. She made this confession yesterday(being Friday).<img alt=\"\" src=\"Vshegeeveh\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;She confessed that she is a member of a local cult group known as the<strong> &quot;sky queens&quot;</strong>. The seventeen-year-old girl later identified as Promise Idorenyin an SSS2 student of community secondary school, Ikot Ewa, in Akpabuyo local government area of the state was paraded alongside her lover a man of 38 years old who eventually turned out to be the man that gave her the local gun she was caught with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Okon Effiong a father of six children from two different women admitted that he and the 17 years old girl were indeed lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most shocking part was that he claimed that the parent&nbsp;of the girl was aware of the fact that their daughter was in a relationship with him. Although initial reports suggested that Promise had gone to school with the gun to shoot one of her teachers who had disciplined her for dyeing her hair, the 38-year-old man refuted the reports saying that she intended taking the gun to the blacksmith.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Gsjegskssj\" style=\"float:left\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>He furthermore denied giving her the gun. Effiong claimed that he had planned to marry her but the girl disapproved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He said, <strong>&quot; her parents know about us, and I have been helping the mother and the girl.&quot;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There were some contradictions in their statements, while the man claimed that he took the gun to the girl&#39;s house where he sometimes sleeps, he claimed not to have given her the gun. Promise on the other hand said that the gun was for repairs but she did not know any blacksmith in the community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The commissioner of police in the state had earlier on paraded a total of 13 suspects before the newsmen pledged the commitment and determination of the police in fighting crime in the state. Saturday Nation gathered that the state government plans on prosecuting Effion and reorientating and rehabilitating Promise.</p>','crossriver crime','pics/cultist.png','2021-02-21 16:37:02.264205','2021-02-21 16:37:02.264243','2021-02-21 17:56:10.233666','published',651,4,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(49,'Opinion: Message To All Christians And Muslims In Nigeria','opinion-message-to-all-christians-and-muslims-in-nigeria','<p>Some of the most unforgettable tragic events that took place in Nigeria are as a result of religious disputes. Mostly between the Christians and the Muslims. The federal government has tried to put in all efforts in order to sell that these two religious groups set aside their differences and make Nigeria move forward.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Gjsvjsv\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now today I will be suggesting ways in which the federal government can totally eradicate the seemingly unending disputes between the Christians and the muslims.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Sjsvsjsbsj\" style=\"float:left\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Punishment: His excellency,the president should sign and pass a bill which would determine what would be done to people who start such riots that end in chaos and destruction. In my suggestion this bill should be reviewed by the senate and all possible ways of tackling this would be resolved alongside issuance of stiff punishment that would discourage all other people who are trying to venture into this same act.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Sjdvdjdbej\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Public Address: Just as the former president of the United States of America, Donald Trump addressed his people during their time of desolation which was during the lockdown period on a daily basis,the federal government should also address the people with whom they lead.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Visiting other religious groups as a president:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Just as the pope and chief Imams in the world visit other religious groups around them so too the president should. This is to promote the love and unity amongst the religious groups in Nigeria, just as the former president Goodluck Ebele Jonathan did.<img alt=\"\" src=\"Djvdjev\" style=\"float:left\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nigeria is a blessed country, blessed with all the resources we can think of but corruption is our major stumbling block in our progress. I think with these points the rate of religious killings would be reduced, the federal government should look considerably into this matter and come up with ideas that will help curb the spread of this social sickness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please do ensure to click on the follow button to get updated when next I post. Thank you.</p>','religion christian muslim','pics/images_-_2021-02-17T194329.732.jpeg','2021-02-21 18:48:58.615486','2021-02-21 18:48:58.615528','2021-02-22 17:12:00.477506','published',651,29,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(55,'5 Common Lifestyle Habits That Can Cause You To Age Faster','5-common-lifestyle-habits-that-can-cause-you-to-age-faster','<p>It is important to live healthy as a way to promote long life, especially to keep our aging process in check. It is also important that we keep our body, minds, and brain working sharp and vibrant. Below are some surprising lifestyle habits that actually cause us to age faster.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Using a hard brush and scrubs.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Using hard brush and scrubs may cause you to age faster as they may injure or scrape your upper epidermis layer. A scrub may end up leaving your skin burned, dry, flaky, red, and blotched and this is not favorable to the skin!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Being physically inactive.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Exercises are physical activities that are done in order to become more active, stronger, and healthier. Having regular exercises is a part of the best weight loss options. Actively involving oneself in physical exercises as it&#39;s beneficial importance, as it greatly boosts the immune system, helps prevent inflammation, improves mental health, and helps us burn excess fat and calories. However, always exercising for the sole purpose of weight loss will cause you to lose the other important benefits of exercises to the body, and you might surprisingly look older than you used to.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Using products containing strong chemicals may also cause you to age faster.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Avoiding fatty foods.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It is ideal to avoid calorie-dense trans fat foods like red meat, fries, ice cream, carbonated drinks, and waffles. However, you should never make the mistake of cutting down unsaturated fats in your diet, as doing so could cause you to age even faster. Unsaturated fats are found in healthy oils like pure olive oil, coconut oil, pure vegetable oils, fish and fish oils, and nuts.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Stress.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Extensive studies and research have shown and proven that stress (both short-term and long-term physical and psychological stress) can cause premature aging and quick aging. This is because when you are stressed, your body produces cortisol, a naturally occurring glucocorticoid hormone that is released mainly at the time of stress. Cortisol is often called &quot;the stress hormone&quot;. However, cortisol can greatly accelerate your aging process as Increased cortisol production can lead to the appearance of lines, rosacea wrinkles, and age spots.&nbsp;Smoking, excessive drinking, and eating unhealthy foods will also accelerate your process of aging, leaving your appearance older.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','beauty tips','pics/images_-_2021-02-20T101207.981.jpeg','2021-02-22 09:11:36.706135','2021-02-22 09:11:36.706191','2021-02-22 16:54:49.226856','published',657,21,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(56,'How To Make Strawberry And Honey Popcorn At Home','how-to-make-strawberry-and-honey-popcorn-at-home','<p>Popcorn is a popular snack enjoyed by all and sundry around the world. This is so because of its crunchy and delicious taste. It can come in many flavors such as milk, chocolate, strawberry, honey, and lots more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are also so many toppings that can be used to make popcorn consumption an unforgettable experience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This article will cover the process of making the various flavors of popcorn, but before then this is how to make a simple popcorn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ingredients needed include the popcorn kernels, vegetable oil, and salt to taste.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method of preparation</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In a clean saucepan, add some oil to the pan and allow it to heat gradually. Add some popcorn kernels to the oil and allow it to pop.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure the pot is properly covered so the kernels don&#39;t pop out of the pot and get all over the place. Shake at intervals and allow the kernels to properly.</li>\r\n	<li>Place the pot on low heat so it does not get burnt. Once the popping sound stops remove from the heat and transfer to a bowl and salt to taste. The simple popcorn is ready.</li>\r\n	<li>There are many flavors of popcorn as earlier mentioned but the strawberry and honey would be covered in this article.</li>\r\n	<li>Honey popcorn</li>\r\n	<li>Transfer the already prepared popcorn to a bowl and add some melted butter and mix.</li>\r\n	<li>Add the honey and mix. Spread them out on a greased baking pan and dry them in an oven.</li>\r\n	<li>Remove from the oven and separate the clumps of popcorn into sizeable pieces. The honey popcorn is ready.</li>\r\n	<li>Strawberry popcorn</li>\r\n	<li>This recipe is really simple can be prepared in the following steps.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In a clean pan, add some butter and allow it to melt. Add the sugar and the strawberry flavored gelatin.</li>\r\n	<li>Mix properly to prevent lumps, transfer to the bowl containing the popcorn, and mix.</li>\r\n	<li>You can add more if you need an even intense color. Transfer to a greased baking pan so it does not stick to the pan. Dry in an oven and allow to cool.</li>\r\n	<li>Separate the popcorn into small pieces. The strawberry popcorn is ready for consumption. You can also top the popcorn with anything you like such as sprinkles, chocolate, peanuts, and sweets too.</li>\r\n	<li>I am sure you liked the recipe and found it really simple. Remember to like and follow for more updates on your favorite meals.</li>\r\n</ul>','#food #popcorn','pics/IMG_20210222_104614.jpg','2021-02-22 09:48:35.771259','2021-02-22 09:48:35.771333','2021-02-23 10:35:42.347991','published',669,28,1,0,'unlimited','Headline can be made more captivating. Revise and resubmit',0,1),(65,'Make Your Own Homemade Pizza Using This Recipe','make-your-own-homemade-pizza-using-this-recipe','<p>Have you ever wanted to have a delicious box of pizza, but ran out of cash on a weekend? Never worry, because this post is specially made for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pizza is one of the meals that are enjoyed by many. It is a flatbread that is lavishly garnished with lots of toppings that you can&#39;t resist.&nbsp;The pizza ingredients are divided into two, which include the pizza dough and the pizza sauce.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Procedures for preparing homemade pizza.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>These are the ingredients needed for the pizza sauce and they include garlic, white onions, olive oil, water, Italian seasoning, shredded cheese, brown sugar, and red wine.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Chop the garlic and white onions nicely into little bits and set aside. In a clean saucepan, add some olive oil and add garlic, and white onions.</li>\r\n	<li>Allow to cook for some time then, nicely ground tomatoes, add the water, Italian seasoning, shredded cheese, brown sugar, and red wine, and allow to simmer.</li>\r\n	<li>Cook the sauce for some time and remove it from the heat.</li>\r\n	<li>These are the ingredients for the pizza dough. Flour, warm water, yeast, sugar, olive oil, salt, shredded cheese, Italian seasoning.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In a clean bowl, add the warm water and sprinkle some sugar. Add the yeast and allow it to react with the sugar.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In a separate bowl, sift in flour and salt together and add to the yeast mixture. Add the Italian seasoning, cheese, olive oil, and mix together.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Transfer to a floured board and knead with your hands. Place the dough on a pizza board and flatten it in a circular form.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Cover with kitchen plastic and allow to rest. Wash the bell peppers, pepperoni, grated cheese, diced tomatoes, onions, or anything you like.</li>\r\n	<li>Chop the vegetables and set them aside. Remove the covering and place the tomato sauce on the dough.</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinkle lots of shredded cheese, bell peppers, pepperoni, diced tomatoes, onions and bake until golden brown in a preheated oven.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The pizza is all set for the eating. I am sure you liked the recipe, don&#39;t forget to try it out sometime.</p>','#food #pizza','pics/IMG_20210224_094925.jpg','2021-02-24 10:36:40.718617','2021-02-24 10:36:40.718711','2021-02-27 19:18:56.676660','published',669,28,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(70,'Review Of Moreme Hub Publishing Guidelines | March, 2020','review-of-moreme-hub-publishing-guidelines-march-2020','<p>In the past month, we noticed a lot of plagiarized articles were sent for publication. It is important to note that Moremehub will no longer accept articles that have less than 85% unique paragraphs. Content creators should note that articles that are rejected would be removed from the creator&#39;s dashboard at the end of the month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Content creators should also note that the PPA has been increased to N500.00 and the minimum words required for publication to 800.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, note that articles on food are no longer allowed on moremehub because they are rarely searched online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage our writers to write on Tech(programming), Lifestyle, Gaming and search worthy topics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, articles must contain at least two images. Note that the image should be clear and free from lots of watermarks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All other publishing guidelines remain valid.&nbsp; Creators that adhere to publishing guidelines will be approved to start publishing immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, creators with more than five rejected articles would be banned from further publishing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest.</p>','admin','pics/Screenshot_20210304-012345.jpg','2021-03-04 00:15:08.619252','2021-03-04 00:15:08.619305','2021-03-04 00:33:47.673300','published',1,11,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(71,'Improve Your Crypto Vocab','improve-your-crypto-vocab','<p>1. ALTCOIN: an alternative coin to Bitcoin.&nbsp;&quot;ALTCOIN&quot; is a combination of the two words &quot;atl&quot; &quot;coin&quot; and include all alternative to Bitcoin. The success of Bitcoin as the first peer to peer digital currency paved the way. Many altcoins are trying to target the perceived limitations of bitcoin. An altcoin must have a competitive advantage to succeed against Bitcoin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.NODE: A computer that validates transactions. A node, in the world of digital currency, is a computer that connects to a crypto currency network. The node or the computer supports the network. It supports it through validation and relaying transaction. At the same time, it also gets a copy of the full blockchain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. DEFI: DeFi stands for Decentralized Finance. Decentralized Finance often called DeFi refers to the shift from traditional, centralized financial systems to peer to peer finance enabled by decentralized technologies built on the ethereum blockchain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. KYC: Know your customer. Information gathered by exchanges in compliance with laws.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. SATOSHI: The pseudonym creator and the smallest unit of a Bitcoin. SATOSHI means &quot;smallest unit of Bitcoin (cryptocurrency term)&quot;. SATOSHI is the name given to the smallest unit of the Bitcoin cryptocurrency. It represents one hundred millionth of a Bitcoin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. GAS: A fee which must be paid to execute Ethereum transactions. Gas refers to the fee or pricing value, required to successfully conduct a transaction or execute a contract on the Ethereum blockchain platform. It also refers to the price a Crypto currency user is willing to pay when sending a transaction, or performing a Smart contract function in the Ethereum blockchain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. ATL: All time low. The lowest a coin has ever been. &quot;All time low&quot; is the opposite of ATH which means &quot;All time high&quot;. In the context of crypto currency, it refers to the lowest price milestone that any given coin or token has ever achieved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. Cold wallet: An offline wallet. The simplest description of a cold wallet is a wallet that is not connected to the internet and therefore stands a far lesser risk of being compromised. These wallets can be refered to as offline wallets or hardware wallets. With cold storage, the digital wallet is stored on a platform that is not connected to the internet, thereby protecting the wallet from unauthorized access, cyber hacks and other vulnerabilities to which a system that is connected to the internet is susceptible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Hot wallet: An online wallet.<img alt=\"\" height=\"221\" src=\"/media/post_images/Shay_blog/2021/03/05/images_753EIdV.jpeg\" width=\"330\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>10. BTC: Bitcoin&#39;s ticker symbol.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','pics/100798027_151545336523690_7762518015645314041_n.jpg','2021-03-05 13:48:08.165477','2021-03-05 13:48:08.165530','2021-03-06 15:20:16.973566','rejected',679,1,0,0,'unlimited','Article wholly or partially plagiarized. Repeated violations can cause account termination',0,1),(72,'Learn To Ride A Rollerblade With These Steps.','learn-to-ride-a-rollerblade-with-these-steps','<p>Some weeks ago I had problems riding my Rollerblade as I keep falling off and loose balance. Before you start blading, here are some things you should know about blading and steps you should note.<img alt=\"\" height=\"400\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/06/screenshot_20210306-1509182.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rollerblading is also know as inline skating it is an indoor recreational activity. It us similar to ice skating, it involves gliding on skates that have series of circular wheels set in a straight line without rotating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because balance and control is required, rollerblading can be tough and challenging at the first point if training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are some steps on how to ride a Rollerblade.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Find your balance*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Wear proper safely equipment; Put on a helmet and some knee and elbow pads to protect yourself from bumps, brises and straps. New starting out will require you to get a pair of wrist guards because it will break your fall without hurting yourself our sustaining injuries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Keep your safety gear especially your helmet the entire time you&#39;re skating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Strap on a pair of rollerblades; slip your boot of skates up against your lower shins. Pull the adjustable straps across the boots and through the buckles in the opposite side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Learn how to stand up on a roller skate; Use nearby objects like wall, chair of even tree to help you stand at your feet. If there&#39;s noting around to use for assistance, pull one foot up under and place both hands on the ground in front of you. Climb to your feet one at a time, being careful not to loose balance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Be careful not to let your feet roll out underneath you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Practice standing up on a grass before you jump to a concert. The plush surface will help steady the skates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Place your shoulder-width apart; Once you&#39;re upright, assure a stance similar to how you stand normally. This will be tough but try it. Your toes should be printed straight ahead. If they happen to stray inward or outward while you&#39;re skating, your legs will move with them and you&#39;ll fall down.<img alt=\"\" height=\"710\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/06/screenshot_20210306-1509402.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Balancing successfully on rollerblades is all about making constant adjustments in the angles of your feet and ankles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Pay attention to your feet always and know that your skates are pointed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Practice leaning, pivoting and possibly crouching; This key points will help you generate constant speed and velocity from your blades. Always try to bend your knees slightly and keep hips and ankles nice and loose. Once you&#39;ve got these basics, try picking up one foot and balancing on the other skate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Keep your centre of gravity or equilibrium position lower while skating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Getting in motion*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you&#39;ve got your balance, use these steps to get in constant motion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Move to the pavement; When your feet becomes families with skates, find a flat, level stretch of ground where you have plenty of room to move around. Paved surfaces are ideal for skating since they allow the wheels to roll smoothly. If possible, set yourself up close to a wall or rail that you can hold on to for balance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Start walking slowly in the skates; Pick up one foot and set it down in front of the other. Then repeat with the other foot and challenge yourself to walk from one point to another.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Turn your steps into strokes and small glides; Continue putting one foot in front of the other, only now rather than dropping your feet straight down, push it forward and out. Transfer your weight over one leg to gain balance and hence gliding. This can help to turn back at an angle to give you something to push against.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, by the time you get the hang gliding you should barely be picking up your feet at all.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Use your upper body to maintain your balance; On your first few passes, hold your arms out to your sides and make small adjustments when you feel yourself tipping. You should not bring your arms up higher than your head or let&nbsp; them cross over your body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Learn to pick a speed; To accelerate on blades, simply do the same thing you&#39;ve being doing but only faster. Only skate with as much speed you can control because too much speed can make you fall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Learn how to fall correctly; falling correctly is important in inline skating. As soon as you loose balance lean slightly to one side and let your body collapse gradually. This technique has saved be from serious injuries many times.<img alt=\"\" height=\"710\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/06/screenshot_20210306-1509402_A8E6RC9.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Turning and stopping*</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you&#39;ve got your balance and motion, you also need to stop your blades from displacement.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Lean your body to steer; Start skating at a safe speed and place your feet side-by-side always. Shift your weight over the right edge if both skates to right allowing&nbsp; your ankle to flex. To make a left turn, lean to the left.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Pick up your feet for beginner turns. If you find it difficult to change directions, you can give yourself a little help by pivoting one of the skate to the side you want to go and arcing your other skate to follow the lead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I hope with these few steps you can now skate confidently, why not buy a pair of skates and start rollerblading.</p>','','pics/Screenshot_20210306-1509182.png','2021-03-06 22:57:29.885658','2021-03-06 22:57:29.885706','2021-03-07 00:17:43.522531','rejected',650,7,0,0,'unlimited','Article wholly or partially plagiarized. Repeated violations can cause account termination',0,1),(73,'How To Get Six Packs Fast','how-to-get-six-packs-fast','<p>&nbsp;Everywhere you turn, someone&#39;s wishing the next secret in getting&nbsp;<strong>Six Packs</strong>. While thero no way, except health diet and regular exercise. Such as crunches and planks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Part 1 of 4: Doing crunch Variation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"587\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/screenshot_2021-03-06_1715322.jpg\" width=\"720\" /><strong>1: Doing 4 sets of 12 basic crunches</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;You start by lying on your back with knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Place your hands behind your head, inhale and exhale as you raise your back off the floor. Raise your torso for about 3 seconds, and gently inhale as you lower yourself back to the floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Be sure not to tug your head upward with your hands. Keep your head, neck and back aligned, and avoid arching your lower back as you lift your torso. Repeat the steps to complete a set of 12 crunches. Raise your leg enough to lift your shoulder blades off the ground. Raising yourself all the way to your knees can strain the back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*To increase difficulty, hold a weight over your torso as you do the crunches. Such as with a 5 to 10lb (2B to 4.5kg) to avoid injury.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2: Lift your knees and hips to do reverse crunches</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat in the floor to start. Keep ur hands by your side with your plams facing down. Engage your abs as you exhale and raise your knees over your hips. Keep your knees bent at 90 degree angle as you hold them directly over hips. As you lift your hips and lower back, inhale and exhale with a smooth, controlled motion. As you lower your back and hips, inhale and raise your knees above your hips. Repeat to complete a set of 12 reverse crunches. And at the last one you lower your feet to the floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3: Add bicycle crunch to your routine</strong>. Lay on the floor with your back, and your knees bent and finger tips touching your back head. Make a pedaling motion by driving your left knee toward your torso and extending the other straight. Do well as to inhale and exhale. As you pedal, raise your shoulder blades off the floor and rotate your shoulder to bring your right hand toward your bent left knee. Then, straighten your left leg as you raise your right knee toward your torso. Simultaneously, rotate your legs to bring your bring your left elbow toward your right torso to complete 12 rounds per side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4: Extend your arms to do overhead crunches burn</strong>. Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Straighten your hands above your head with your palms facing up. Your hands should still touch the floor, and your biceps (upper arms) should near your ears. Keeping your arms extended above your head, lift your torso as you are doing a conventional crunch. Remember to keep your head, neck, and spine aligned, and don&#39;t arch your lower back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Part 2 of 4: Mastering Planks Exercise</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"527\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/screenshot_2021-03-06_2318312.jpg\" width=\"720\" /><strong>1: Plank with proper technique to avoid getting injured</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lying on your stomach with your head facing down, forearms and palms on the floor. Breath in and out as you raise your body off the floor so your forearms and toes carry your weight. Elbows bent at 90 degree directly under your shoulders. Engage your core muscles so your head, neck, and spine form a straight line. Try holding the plank for 10 to 15 seconds. Continue to breathe as you hold the position. If 10 to 15 seconds planking isn&#39;t challenging, try increasing the time to 30 to 45 seconds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2: Sculpt your abs and obliques with side planks</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Start by lying on your right side with your right elbow bent directly under your shoulder. Your left leg should be stacked directly over your leg. Inhale and exhale as you engage your core muscles and extend your elbow to a 90 degree angle. Keep your elbow bent directly under your shoulder. Your head, neck and spine should make a straight line.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Continue breathing as you hold the side plank. Try holding it for 30 to 45 seconds, slowly lower yourself back to the starting position, then repeat the steps in your left side. Raise your upper leg off your lower leg as you hold a side plank to increase difficulty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3: Challenge yourself with extended planks</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Start on your stomach as if you were doing a normal plank. Arms above your head with your palms touching the floor, use your fingertips and toes to lift your body off the floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Keep your head in a neutral position so you&#39;re facing the floor throughout the plank. Try to hold the plank for 15 seconds. Continue breathing as you hold the position, then slowly lower yourself back to the floor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Part 3 of 4: Developing a safe routine.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1: Warm up and cool down for 5 to 10 minutes</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may go for a jog, do some jumping jacks, run a mile, or jump rope at the beginning of your workouts. Aerobic exercise will increase&nbsp; blood flow to your muscles, which reduces your risk of injuring yourself. Cool down for about 5 to 10 minutes as to help your muscles recover.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2: Include multiple crunches and plank variations in your routine</strong>. Instead of trying to do 500 crunches, your workout may consist of a number of exercise. A perfect routine may be;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*5 to 10 minute jog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*3 sets of 12 repetition each.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*2 sets of 30 seconds per side(side planks).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*3 sets of 12 repetition per side (bicycle crunches).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3: Do your abs workout routine 3 to 4 times per week</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;As much as you want abs fast, pushing yourself too hard could result in an injury. Find perfect days, in other not to push your muscles too much. Try to focus in being healthy as everyone&#39;s body is unique, but you might see results within a few weeks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;If you&#39;re just starting, it&#39;s wisi to take it slow. Start with 2 sets of 10 repetition for each exercise then gradually move up to 3 sets of 12 reps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4: Burn belly fat</strong>. To see a good result of your hard work, you&#39;ll need to burn fat deposit that cover the abdominal muscles. Do some cardio workout. Jogging, sprinting are good ways to burn fat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Part 4 of 4: Following a fat burning diet</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"459\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/screenshot_2021-03-06_2322082.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1: Pack enough of protein sources into your diet</strong>. Protein build muscle, but it&#39;s important to choose higher fat options. Poultry, fish, eggs and full fat dairy products are examples of good protein foods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2: Fill up on fruits and veggies to cut your calories</strong>. Fruits and veggies are packed with essential nutrients, and they can fill you up without adding calories. Required amoi depends on your age, sex and activity level. When you&#39;re hungry between meals, grab a healthy snack like a banana, apple, or a carrot stick.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3: Cut out sweet and processed foods</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;You won&#39;t see a&nbsp;<strong>six pack</strong>&nbsp;anytime soon if you get most of your calories from processed foods, sweets and fast food. If you need to satisfy your sweet tooth, swap pastries, ice cream and other unhealthy snacks for some peanut butter, and greek yogurt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4: Drink loads of water instead of high calorie drinks</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Staying hydrated is important for your overall health, especially if you&#39;ve started exercising more often. Swapping soda, sweet tea and other high calories drinks help to keep you in a good shape. Go at least 8 cups(1,900mL) of water per day. Keep in mind when the weather is hot, will need to drink a lot of water to make up for excess sweating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Getting abs is not an easy thing to do, so u need to be determined to achieve your goals. And also to stay in a good diet and a healthy living. Stick to these steps of mine and see the great outcome .</p>','','pics/Screenshot_2021-03-06_1714532.jpg','2021-03-07 06:59:30.379796','2021-03-07 06:59:30.379845','2021-03-08 00:37:47.675479','rejected',685,27,0,0,'unlimited','Bad Images, Headline can be made more captivating, Revise and resubmit',1,1),(74,'How To Build A Website (Programmer Tips)','how-to-build-a-website-programmer-tips','<p>Are you a potential web builder or designer? Or do you have the ambition to build websites and apps such as Facebook,WhatsApp,YouTube and so on? Then you have come to the right place. Today I shall be teaching you the basics you need to know about website development, what you need in order to build a strong,attractive and most importantly a working website. So I urge us all to sit close and read carefully if you want to understand the basics.<img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t075747104.jpeg\" width=\"640\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, what is a website? A website is simply a collection of web pages. This very site is a website,that entails that this site too is made up of web pages. In simpler terms a website is like a book made up of many pages and features. So how are websites made? Just as the definition implies,a website is a collection of web pages,and what do you do with a page of a book? You write on it,so websites are made by writing. This might sound odd because,you would probably be wondering how we use writing to create the designs,and even some objects in a site,but the whole truth is that everything you see was created by writing. But it is not the regular pen and paper writing but a special type of writing known as <strong>coding</strong> or <strong>programming.</strong> What is Programming? Programming is simply the ability to understand and execute a given task on a computer through the use of the language of the computer. Language of the computer? That sounds insane right? But yes just as we humans have languages such as English,Igbo,Yoruba,Hausa and so on, so too the computer has its own languages. So what is or are these languages of the computer? In the human race there are millions of languages spoken world wide,this is also likened to the language of the computer, there are various languages such as Python, java,HTML,hack,CSS,c,c++,php and so many more,but the universal language which can be understood by all computers is known as the mother language of the computer. This is also likened to English language and French. So these various languages serve different purposes. An example is HTML which is used for the creation of websites and webpages, javascript is used for apps and games and so on and so forth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But for the case study we shall be looking at HTML because it is in line with your dream career.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HTML</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HTML is an abbreviation for &#39;HyperText Mark-up Language&#39; it is a programming language used for the creation of web pages. And just as we have earlier discussed, a website is a combination of web pages,so in order to build a website you have to start by building or creating each individual page. You cannot just manufacture a book without starting with single pages. Many people do not actually consider HTML to be a programming language because it is actually the easiest of all. This means that of all the programming languages there is,HTML is the simplest and easiest to learn. To be able to build your website you need to learn this language,as I have earlier said it doesn&#39;t really mean you would start.speaking weird or saying some strange diabolic words, all you need to do is to write. On average it shouldn&#39;t take you more than two months to completely master learning this language.<img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t075747104_0EhS3V9.jpeg\" width=\"640\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>But you do not solely need HTML to build a working and attractive website,HTML only builds the website but to design and add other colourful and attractive features you need another newly formed language known as CSS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CSS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CSS is also an abbreviation which signifies or stands for &#39;Cascaded Style Sheet&#39;. It deals mainly on designs,fonts,tone,intensity and other amazing features which makes websites look wonderful and eye catching. But does this mean you would also have to learn this language? Yes of course, but the advantage is that there are a lot of similarities between CSS and HTML being that they both work hand in hand. <img alt=\"\" height=\"444\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/5fca533970f52_1.png\" width=\"753\" />Provided you have fully learnt HTML,CSS shouldn&#39;t take you more than a week of consistency to learn. With these two languages as a programmer,you can build any type of website you need. One of the best places to learn these languages is at &#39;w3schools&#39;,this is an online website that was designed to teach people all they need to know about all the computer languages and you get to write down some codes yourself.<img alt=\"\" height=\"452\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t075812999.jpeg\" width=\"678\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an upcoming programmer,I would advise you to first start with these two languages before you can progress to the more difficult ones like JavaScript, c++ and the rest. Also web building is also a sure way of getting money because there are many people all over the&nbsp; world who are willing to pay to have someone build them a site. So if you can learn this language you would be able to earn a living.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At this juncture you can now take a sip of the cold beer beside you and kindly smash the follow button and sign up with this site in order to get updated on more programming tips and advice. Thank you.</p>','','pics/5fca533970f52_1.png','2021-03-07 07:24:23.158212','2021-03-07 07:24:23.158282','2021-03-08 18:10:17.954829','rejected',677,11,0,0,'unlimited','Article does not show in-depth knowledge, consider writing on making a website for free. Revise',1,1),(75,'How To Remember Anything Without Stress (Student Tips)','how-to-remember-anything-without-stress-student-tips','<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"246\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t083246896.jpeg\" width=\"370\" />Many students are faced with the challenge of not being able to recall what they have been taught. This does not generally imply that they are bad students but it reveals the capacity of their brain to the outer public. Today we shall be looking at ways in which students can build up their brain capacities and turn out to become outstanding students among their peers. So if you are a student who unfortunately falls into the category of students we are going to be looking at today,then I urge you to sit back and listen carefully also share this article to your friends who might also be needing aid in this course.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Remembrance test: What does this mean? I personally carryout a remembrance test before I go for any exams. A remembrance test is a test where you strain your brain to recall events without looking for clues or checking for answers. In other words,before you read for an exam,try to first recall what you ha e been taught before you open the book. What you remember determines how large your brain capacity is,first and foremost try to recall the topics you have treated,then definitions,then types,examples and so on. Then when you feel you cannot recall any further you can now open your book to read. Now the sweetest part of this is that,those ones you recalled without opening your book,you would barely forget them,in fact the possibility of you forgetting them is 1%. Why? Because you stressed you brain to dugout this information&#39;s,so it would be difficult for the brain to hide them again because it does not want to undergo such stress again.<img alt=\"\" height=\"479\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t083302460.jpeg\" width=\"640\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Constant and Continous Reading: Do not solely resort to opening your books only during times of examinations or tests. Open your books regularly, get conversant with the pages and the wordings, now why is this necessary, some times you might just forget certain information&#39;s, but because you are conversant with that book,once you recall the page you think you saw it it would begin to reveal itself to you.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Seeking other methods or definitions: Now one if the biggest challenge Nigerian students fail to achieve is the belief in monopoly of knowledge. Most students only stick to the formulas or definitions given by their teachers. This is not generally bad,but as a student you should be able to research other ways,methods or definitions you can use to define a particular subject matter. Also one if the best traits a student can develop is the ability to devise your own definition to things and otifer solutions your way. This builds self confidence in the students other than solely depending on the definitions of their tutors.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Symbolism: in this context,symbolism refers to the use of things,object or people as a means of recalling certain events. Just the way wound scares serve as a reminder to a certain time when you got injured so too the use of symbs is necessary for students. When you are being taught and you feel you might not be able to recall it,use objects or people around you to do so.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Abbreviations: Abbreviations can be defined as the use of a part to represent a whole. This simply means that you use one part of something or an object to represent the entire object just as the cases of synecdoche and metonymy. So how does abbreviations help or aid students remember things quickly? When you use abbreviations there is a high chance of remembering a long sentence faster than when you try to cram them. Just as the abbreviation for the United States Of America is USA so too students can relate these to certain topics and sentences an example is the &quot;IPMAT&quot; in biology used to represent the stages of cell division which individually stand for Interphase,Prophase,Metaphase,Anaphase and Telophase. Another good example is &quot;MR NIGER ACD&#39;&#39; used to represent the characteristics of living things which are Movement, Respiration,Nutrition,Irritation, Growth,Excretion,Reproduction, Adaptation, Competition and Death. This is a clear example of how important abbreviations are to students. Also if you find it difficult to remember things quickly then abbreviations will serve as a sure remedy for you.<img alt=\"\" height=\"451\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t083225969.jpeg\" width=\"680\" /></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>As a student forgetfulness is a sign that you are not conversant with your books,so you need to sit up and read because you are still young,but as an adult,forgetting things easily is not bad because as you advance in age the body weakens and so also does the brain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With thee few points I do hope that your capacity of educational facts accumulations would be increased. Please do ensure to click on the subscribe button to get updated when next I post. Thank you.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T083302.460.jpeg','2021-03-07 07:37:07.729415','2021-03-07 07:37:07.729571','2021-03-12 13:35:57.981300','rejected',677,9,0,0,'unlimited','Significant amount of plagiarism found, article not up to 800 words, spelling and grammatical errors found',0,1),(76,'3 Crucial Things To Note Before Applying For International Scholarships in 2021','3-crucial-things-to-note-before-applying-for-international-scholarships-in-2021','<p>There are many scholarship opportunities out there that are open to both internal and international students. Many students who are not financially balanced are usually faced with the problem of not being able to further their studies and pursue their dream goals, hence the need for scholarships.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>WHAT IS A SCHOLARSHIP?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A scholarship is an award presented to an individual by an organization or sometimes an individual who promises to take care of any monetary demands concerning the education of the recipient. One of the best scholarships to win is a full scholarship and I shall be explaining to you briefly some of the things you need to know before applying for scholarships.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before we move into details I would greatly be please if you could just smash the follow button at the end of this article to get updated when next I make a post. So we shall quickly be looking at the different types of scholarships. There are two main types of scholarships, they are;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Full scholarships</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Part scholarships</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FULL SCHOLARSHIPS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A full-time scholarship is a type of scholarship that is 100% covered ranging from your travel cost, feeding, books, and most importantly 100% school fee coverage. In this type of scholarship, all you need to do is to pass their exams and if you are lucky,&nbsp;&nbsp;you get awarded, just pack your bags and go, you do not need to bother about visas and anything concerning money, they will take care of all that. All you need is to just wait for when your flight has been booked, kiss everyone goodbye and depart. Numerous organizations all over the world provide full-time scholarships such as MasterCard foundation, commonwealth scholarships, government scholarships, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PART SCHOLARSHIPS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike the full-time scholarships, these scholarships do not cover 100% of your tuition fees and many of them do not even include travel costs, accommodation, and so on. So if the tuition fee of the university you applied to is $100,000 and the scholarship covers 50% then the organization would be responsible for $50,000 and you would have to pay the rest. So these are the two types of scholarships we have, both are good and you should apply for both because you do not know how lucky you might be. So now that we have gotten a little knowledge about the types of scholarships, what are some of the basic things we should know about scholarships and their application?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SCHOLARSHIP APPLICATION PROCESSES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are certain things you need to know before you apply for any scholarship be it part-time or full scholarships. If you are applying for an international scholarship to countries like the United States of America, England, and other English-speaking countries, there is a 99% chance that an English proficiency exam result will be demanded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WHAT IS AN ENGLISH PROFICIENCY EXAM?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is an international exam set by the English-speaking countries in other to know the level of understanding of their language (English language) by immigrants into their nation. So before applying for any scholarship, you should have written this exam, it is commonly referred to as TOEFL or the alternative known as IELTS. Also in some cases, you will be required to sit for SAT or GREs, these exams are meant to test your mathematics background.<img alt=\"graduation cap on money\" height=\"451\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t084752990.jpeg\" width=\"680\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>AFTER ENGLISH PROFICIENCY EXAM, WHAT NEXT?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assuming you have written the exams listed above, what&#39;s next? Always endeavor to read the eligibility part of scholarships, do not just jump into the application, first read the eligibility part to see if you are eligible for such scholarships.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why is this necessary?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is because some people waste their time applying only to find out that their country wasn&#39;t included in the scholarship grant. So it is good you read the eligibility part to check if your country is included in the scholarship, if yes then you can apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The next thing you need to take note of is the deadline for submission. Every scholarship has a deadline, so you need to check the scholarship deadline before submission (<strong>Note:</strong> it is important you submit your form when the deadline is still far because you stand a chance to be selected other than waiting for a later date).<img alt=\"Graduation cap in books\" height=\"415\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t084814221.jpeg\" width=\"739\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also never make the mistake of submitting a fake report of yourself, or duplicating your result in other to be selected. If you do this and your cover is blown open you stand a chance of losing the scholarship entirely. Always try to be genuine, if you feel your high school grades are not high enough, you can rewrite&nbsp;them in other to get a better one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you and I wish you success in your application.</p>','scholarship, education, toefl,studyabroad','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T084752.990.jpeg','2021-03-07 07:54:08.336204','2021-03-07 07:54:08.336260','2021-03-10 00:40:23.380039','published',677,9,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(77,'How Not To Read For An Exam (Student Tips)','how-not-to-read-for-an-exam-student-tips','<p>There are many ways students read for exams but today we shall be looking at ways students should not read for exams. Yes you read the right words &quot;the ways students should <strong>not</strong> read for exams&quot;. Note,we shall begin by explaining the word exam,exam or examination has many diverse meanings but for the sake of simplicity we shall be taking a very simple definition.<img alt=\"\" height=\"462\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t094829423.jpeg\" width=\"664\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An exam is a test which is set by a tutor to test the level of understanding of his/her students. This generally means that exams are basically tests meant to determine how well you know or understand a subject matter. Now,on a more ideal note,students are not actually meant to read for exams,yes because you are expected to write down what you know according to what you understand. But being that exams are usually set on a particular date,students are usually made to prepare ahead of such exams by reading. But there are many wrong methods of reading students exhibit that we shall be looking at today.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Cramming: This one is a very popular practice among students. Cramming is a funny practice where students force lines into their heads(brain). But this practice often helps students pass some tests and exams,so why is it bad? Now,cramming is evidence that you never understood what was taught by your tutor. Watch and monitor the outstanding students in your class or course mates,now when you understand a subject matter you do not need to give the exact definition you were given by the tutor in your note. This is what students fail to understand,hence they resort to cramming. This is also coupled with the fact when you forget a single word from what you crammed,there is a high tendency for you to totally forget everything.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Reading a few minutes before exams: Yes,this one is quite shocking right? You are expected to read at least 2 hours before your exams then you have a short nap,when you wake up you have a little revision before going to the exam hall where you relax and not stress your brain anymore. This is because reading a few minutes before an exam can cause a lot of confusion <strong>in some cases.</strong> There have been cases of students who tried to devise a few lines just before the exam papers were dispensed,but became confused as a result of exam fright and so on. The few minutes you have before your exam starts should be a few minutes of prayer and mind relaxation.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Short hand reading: Short hand reading in this context refers to the process where a student just reads a few lines of a topic and enters the next. In this case, a student would just read the part of the note they feel is most important and neglect the rest. This is only advisable when the note is excessively large then I would advise you engage in shorthand reading,but if not you should not engage in such risk,this is because some teachers are unpredictable. You might never know where the next question would come from.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>These are but few of some of the ways you should stop reading. The most important thing to take note of when reading is that you are reading to understand and not just to pass. Read because you truly want to know what happened and not because you want to get high grades. Also I shall enlighten you on a very important tip you need to know in the course of reading for exams. One important thing you need to know is that when reading for exams you need to take a lot of water,yes drink a lot of water. Water helps in refreshing the brain thereby aiding you avoid fatigued easily. Whenever you are reading and you notice that you are getting tired or you are not apprehending as much as you did when you started, the best thing to do is to have a glass of water and take a minute break before you can continue.<img alt=\"\" height=\"401\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/fb_img_16151061227392803.jpg\" width=\"534\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As I have earlier emphasized,read to know and not to pass. One of the best ways of getting a higher IQ is by doing research,discovering things by yourself,for mathematics sort out equations by yourself and you will discover that those equations would not easily depart from you because you figured them out yourself. Cramming will not help you,it only defines the kind of student you are,a lazy type. Yes,it is only lazy students who cram to pass. Always give every exam your best,put your knowledge to test and watch a great improvement in your academic life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please click on the follow button to get updated when next I post,also subscribe to this site so that notifications on relevant articles would be sent directly to your devices. Thank you.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T094829.423.jpeg','2021-03-07 08:52:30.284596','2021-03-07 08:52:30.284649','2021-03-08 00:39:29.282016','rejected',677,9,0,0,'unlimited','Rework Headline, Click to revise and resubmit',1,1),(78,'How To Restore Your Business In Times Of Financial Crises','how-to-restore-your-business-in-times-of-financial-crises','<p>Today I shall be sharing with you some sure ways of sustaining, regaining and rising your business from the scratch. Many businesses are suffering today,so it deem fit to share this article with you if you eventually fall in that category.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now what are the possible things that can lead to the closure or economic imbalance in a business? They could range from debts,theft,liquidation and so on,but what exactly leads to these things,that shall be our first discussion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>CAUSES OF BUSINESS FAILURE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Businesses fail for diverse reasons,but we shall be looking at but a few dangerous business killers that can lead to liquidation and closure of business;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Debt: When a business owner has a huge amount of debt in other words,is owing a huge amount of money, his business tends to be unstable except he or she is fortunate enough in such a way the borrowed money actually helped in raising his business. But debt is one thing every business owner should run away from. Unless you are faced with a serious challenge do not borrow or land in debt.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Profit eaters: These are a special set of people who live on &#39;eat as you come&#39;,in other words,whatever is coming into their pockets as sales,they consume. You should totally run away from this. Because people who engage In this have no future for their business. As a business owner one of your major priorities is to expand in your business but how can you do that when you eat both your capital?</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">The late comers: Many business owners are fond of coming late to their places of assignment. Now the more you come Kate the more unserious your customers find you to be. You are the one who is supposed to be waiting for your customers in your shop and not vice versa. Late coming kills business,comes early and makes sales.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"443\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t095412380.jpeg\" width=\"692\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Solutions To Business Failures</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What happens when your business fails? Do you just give up on it? No,there&nbsp; are many things you should try out before considering quitting your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Promotion: This involves advertising your business to the public, when most organisations notice that they are losing ground,they begin to advertise their products to the public, you too should do the same,you should not necessarily go to the television and being to make an advert but you can promote your business ESS with your mouth,make people know what you sell,do not be ashamed to make known your business constituent to people when you meet,give them your business card in case they might be needing it some time in the future.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Discounts: Discount is a business strategy where a business organisation reduces the prices of their commodities in order to attract more customers. This is one of the reasons why business is termed as a risk,because the company or organisation would have tocompetitions.&nbsp; a lot of profit in order to regain her customers,and when these customers come back they can now gradually raise the prices. So too this applies to every other business owners out there,you do not necessarily need to beg your customers to return to you but you can stimulate the change you want by creating a temporal discount in the prices of your commodities. The only painful thing about discount is that you should be ready to face loss,but at the end if such period you will realise that the good it will bring will outweigh the bad because success comes after a lot of failures.<img alt=\"\" height=\"246\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t083246896_tBZGH5I.jpeg\" width=\"370\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Competitions or giftings: One of the best ways of retaining a lot of customers is by giving them gifts. It could be in form of competitions such that one lucky customer would be gifted a star price and so on. With these you are sure to retain a whole lot of customers. People are generally stimulated by free or almost free things, and they are generally moved to try out their luck in such competitions.So you could set such competitions in such a way that purchasing one of your least sold commodities would be the ticket.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Selling Quality Products: When you sell inferior products in place of original ones,your business would fall spontaneously because people do not generally like being cheated. In fact this is one of the fastest ways of destroying your business,how? You ask,because the moment just one customer realises that you are selling an inferior product, the speed at which that news would circulate round your other customers would be a shocker to you. So sell quality over quantity. Many business men are only driven by the passion to refill their shops non are interested in selling quality,but they tend yo forget that 99 days is for the the if,one day is for the owner.</li>\r\n</ol>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T095412.380.jpeg','2021-03-07 09:06:51.030372','2021-03-07 09:06:51.030430','2021-03-07 09:06:51.030446','pending',677,17,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,0),(79,'How To Earn Big On YouTube (Beginners Tips)','how-to-earn-big-on-youtube-beginners-tips','<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"454\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t095536620.jpeg\" width=\"675\" />YouTube is one of the most visited sites in the world with more than 1 billion visitors which is about 1/7 of the worlds total population. Aside the fact that you can stream videos on YouTube,one of the most interesting things about YouTube is that you can also make money on YouTube. You can make money on YouTube by uploading original videos on YouTube, the reason the word original is used is because,YouTube promotes contents that are original and genuine and not those that are stolen from other peoples work/labour.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Like every other company,YouTube has its policies and criteria before you can start earning money,you cannot just upload videos and await alert messages on your phone. First you have to gain a maximum of 1000 active subscribers. This is just like having 1000 followers on Facebook or Instagram. This criteria is not that difficult to gain but the second criteria is what determined your earning potential. Aside the 1000 subscribers, you also need to have a total of 4000 watch hours, what this simply means is that your videos should have been watched by an estimated 4000 watch hours,that is 1 hour four thousand times. This criteria is not that easy to achieve but the only way to meet up with this is to make your videos long.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you post a one hour long video,and you are lucky enough to have more than 10000 views and about 1000 watched the video from the very beginning to the end,then you have already completed &frac14; of the total time required. But if you always post short videos,the possibility if you monitising quick is going to be very slim.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now,how do you create a YouTube channel? All you need to do is to search for <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com\" style=\"text-decoration-line:none\">www.YouTube.com</a> on the internet and search for create account,if you have a valid email account this should not be a problem. But if you don&#39;t have an email account yet,then I urge you to create one immediately. When you have finally registered you can now go to play store and download the YouTube app and YouTube studio app. These two apps work hand in hand and I am going to be explaining what I mean by that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now you need the YouTube app to upload your videos in the internet and you need the YouTube studio app to edit those videos. So,when you have created a video all you need to do us to enter the YouTube app and click on the plus(+) sign below the screen then two options would pop up,me would be &quot;upload video&quot; and the other would be &quot;go live&quot; ,I guess we know the one to click,of course you would click upload video,then you can select your video and also choose the category of people that can access your videos,by choosing either &quot;yes this video is made for kids&quot; or &quot;no,this video is not made for kids&quot; then you can upload it on the internet.<img alt=\"\" height=\"368\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t081334089.jpeg\" width=\"668\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now after uploading the video,the next thing to do is to create a thumbnail, a thumbnail is the picture that people see when they search for things related to your video. The thumb nail must be attractive and be able to catch the eyes of viewers. So after creating a thumbnail,you can now enter the YouTube studio app and you would see the video you uploaded,then you click on edit and click on the pencil like figure of the picture then you choose upload custom thumbnail, custom thumbnail means your personal thumbnail, because what YouTube does is that they give random thumbnails to people,which are usually not attractive. So to choose your own thumbnail you have to click on choose custom thumbnail then you can select the picture you edited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One other important thing to note is that you should try as much as you can in every way you can by every means you can to avoid plagiarism. Plagiarism is the act of stealing other peoples video and posting them in your channel,you should always remember that YouTube has an advanced AI (artificial intelligence) that can detect plagiarised videos,and if you are caught, which must certainly happen,you will not be able to monetize your channel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even songs are often plagiarised, but that does not affect your monetization abilities. You need to learn the art of being fair,original and genuine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this you can be up and running and if you are consistent would also become apart of youtues partner program which would enable you to monetize. In our next video I shall be teaching you how to get monetized in less than a month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please subscribe to this site so that you would get updated when next I post.</p>','','pics/youtube.webp','2021-03-07 09:13:42.387895','2021-03-07 09:13:42.387940','2021-03-07 09:13:42.387956','pending',677,11,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,0),(80,'How To Become Successful In Life And Fulfil Your Dreams.','how-to-become-successful-in-life-and-fulfil-your-dreams','<p>Every individual wishes to be successful and rich, and not to be poor and not be able to achieve dreams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Success requires a strong&nbsp; sense of determination and passion for a particular goal. This goals can only be achieved through hardwork and prayers.<img alt=\"\" height=\"470\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210307-1020542.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A successful man lives a life of fulfilment and joy, and not of regret, pain and agony. No man will love to teach or pray for his child to become poor and unsuccessful. We all wish well for our children and loved ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being successful takes knowledge, skill and of course education. Without further ado, here are the key ways to becoming a successful individual.<img alt=\"\" height=\"361\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210307-1020312.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Build A High Self-esteem.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Building a high self-esteem requires an individual to be bold, confident and brave for what he stand for. You should have a strong sence of confidence in yourself if you want to become successful and hence achieving your dreams. Self-esteem is gold because if you have that, nobody will stop you from striving to be the best. You just need to believe in yourself and do what you know best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Stay Positive.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>​​​​​​</strong>The power of positively is crucial and cannot be over emphasis in fulfilling your dreams. Try to see the things at a brighter side and perspective, there should be no doubt in your mind when you&#39;re trying and striving to achieve your goals. I&#39;ll advise you to keep away from peers or people who will make you doubt your goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being positive and confident has helped me passed many exams, test and interviews. It can be a bridge to you success so stay positive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Preserver and never quit.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you set your goals and it&#39;s not working as planned or desired, keep tryiny and learn from your failures. Don&#39;t ever quite on your dreams that you love most because these dreams are part of you. Don&#39;t let it go for any reason or person, just work harder and learn from your mistakes as this will make you a better person.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Form a winning habit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From tender age you should learn the act of winning and not loosing. Winners succeed in what ever there are doing therefore, you should developed a sense of winning in you. Make winning a normal thing in you life and when you loose, feel bad and make adjustments.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Take Risks.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wealthy businessmen you know today take risks to improve their business. People such as Aliko Dangote, Jeff Benzos, Mark Zukerberg and other rich businessmen sacrifice risk for success. Learn to take risks in improving you business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Be Eager To Learn Everyday.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to become successful in your particular field, learn new things everyday and improve yourself and your abilities. If you&#39;re an entrepreneur and you want development in your business, learn new ways and strategies. Be eager to learn from people who are above you as this will make you better equipped with knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Stay Focused And Don&#39;t Divert.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Staying focused helps a lot, you should not be multitasked in being successful, choose a particular dream you wish to fulfill and don&#39;t change your mind. Let your dreams guide you in choosing goals that will improve your life. Make your goals and wishes presise and don&#39;t ever divert from what you want to achieve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Stop looking For A Mentor.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&#39;ll advise you to forget about mentorship, be your motivation and motivate yourself. You know your strengths and weaknesses so why not balance them. Don&#39;t look up to anybody as you mentor if you want to become successful, just look up to God because he alone can grant your heart desires.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9. Stop wishing and start doing.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This it the same thing you&#39;re told in the gymnasium, and you should apply it in your whole life generally while striving to become successful. I&#39;ll advise you to stop the act of just wishing for success, start working and develop yourself to a targeted goal you would love to achieve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10. Strive to be the best.<img alt=\"\" height=\"508\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210307-1021402.png\" width=\"720\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you&#39;ve set your goals try to achieve them and work on how to become the best in what you are doing. This will make your business or activity successful. Keep on learning until you become an expert in that field. I&#39;ll advice you to strive to be the best and trust me when I say the sky will never be your limit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>11. Identify your passion for something.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To become successful, try to identify what you love and have passion for. You also need to improve your skills in this case. This way can make you successful in that particular field or aspect. You can also make cool money from what you love doing with your whole heart.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>12. Be Educated.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Education is what differentiates you from an illiterate. Acquire a high level of education if you what to be successful. There&#39;s a popular saying that &quot;education is the key to success&quot;, this is still a true statement because in most cases, without education you cannot get a good and well paid job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Always improve your educational level to gain more promotion into governmental organizations, this way you can be successful through your educational level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I hope these ways have guided you on how to become successful in life.</p>','','pics/Screenshot_20210307-1020542.png','2021-03-07 12:13:59.563804','2021-03-07 12:13:59.563850','2021-03-08 00:56:17.946454','rejected',650,7,0,0,'unlimited','Bad Images, Make tone secular, write on success stories instead, Revise and resubmit',1,1),(81,'How To Become A Better Footballer','how-to-become-a-better-footballer','<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"500\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/tips-skills-become-successful-football-player_3aAfHD3.jpg\" width=\"955\" />&nbsp;Football is one of the most popular sports with a following of over three and a half billion people. Wherever you turn, at whichever corner of the world you turn to, you&#39;ll find a pitch, a football, and players. Football players are an integral part of the sport. There are countless players who pride themselves as football players. However, to stand out above the rest and be a world recognized player takes a lot. If you&#39;re wondering if you have what it takes to have the world watch you on the pitch, or you want to grow your skills, here are the top tips on how to become a successful professional football player</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Be on a balanced diet.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"459\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/screenshot_2021-03-06_2322082_PMC0L08.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a football player, you need to be on perfect balanced diet so as to make you fit and strong to play. Eating protein based food and other classes of food can do the trick. Eat protein based foods like eggs, poultry, full fat dairy products will put u in go shape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Drink plenty of water.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Water is life&quot;, this means we need water to survive, staying hydrated is important for your overall health, especially if you&#39;ve started playing the sports. Drink at least 4 cups (1,900mL) before a match as it gives you energy. Keep bin mind, when the weather is hot drink enough water, so as to cover for the excess sweating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Practice a lot.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Practice makes perfect. Practicing what you are good at doesn&#39;t only make you good at it but the best.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Find a team.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finding a team is one of the most important aspect in becoming a better player. You need to find a team in which you can practice what you are good at. You can choose a team at your local environment or even at the professional level which you can train.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Make friends on the team.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Making friends on your team is really important as it makes you to understand them. In other for you to be successful in your career you need to be able to associate with them, so as to understand the likes and dislikes of your teammates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Know the rules of the game.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowing the rules if the game is also an essential part of football. You have to understand the game and what it&#39;s all about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Have a player&#39;s kit.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can&#39;t go to school without a uniform, as you can&#39;t play ball without a football kit. In getting a football kit, you have to get what fits well, comfortable, and attractive so as to attract viewers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Motivation.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Motivation goes a long way in making great players. Motivation is what keeps you going even when the odds are stacked against you. When you go back to some of the greatest games in history, you&#39;ll realize a fair share were won by sheer motivation. The whole team may have given up, but a player or two still believed they could do it, and true to the testament, they did. Look for something that motivates you and key in on it. Playing in the World Cup, or winning a trophy can be great motivators. Even when you&#39;re playing a game and it&#39;s not going well, when you picture your motivation, you will be energized to give the game your best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9.Get a mentor.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mentors are those people who are in the same field as you are, and you look up to them and aspire to be like them. In football, there are legends that have gone ahead and set records either at local, regional, or international levels.You should scout your area and see if there is anyone who has achieved what you would want to, and see if they would be willing to help you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10. Give your body time to recover.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many football players are prone to injuries. Some are easy to recover from, while others are career ending. This is due to the exhaustive training and exercising that they undergo on a daily basis. When you are hurt, the first instinct may be to brush it off and continue playing. However, when you do that, you will only cost your team and your body. If you suspect you have an injury or something that needs attention, you should alert the coach, and have a trained medic have a look. When you are fully recovered, you will have your chance on the field. Also, it is important to give your body resting days to help it cope with the regular training and exercising.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; <strong>11. Appreciate</strong>&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;<strong>place of patience.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As mentioned earlier, while setting goals, you need to be realistic. One of the skills that can help you become a successful professional footballer is the ability to exercise patience.Sometimes, the coach may decide to bench you and put in another player. Instead of throwing a fete, you should try and see matters from the coach&#39;s point of view, and try to learn from the player that replaced you.When you exercise patience, you&#39;re able to see matters from a different perspective, and if you can learn from that, then you have got a bright future waiting ahead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the actionable skills that you need to improve on in the field include;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>i. Spatial skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ii. Passing accuracy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iii. Dribbling skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iv. Body control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>v. Tactical knowhow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"816\" src=\"/media/post_images/Daily_News/2021/03/07/functional-training-footballers-entrainement-fonctionnel-footballers-funktionelles-training-fuballer-evo-fitness.jpg\" width=\"1560\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>12. The important take away.The Important Take Away</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clearly, there&#39;s a lot that goes into making a professionally recognized footballer. More even for those who want to have the successes and skillset that matches the great legends of football. The above skills and tactics should help you to dribble past the horde of footballers. Who knows, you just might have the nations chanting your name at the World Cup, it doesn&#39;t get better than that. Good luck.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','pics/tips-skills-become-successful-football-player.jpg','2021-03-07 15:23:58.631598','2021-03-07 15:23:58.631649','2021-03-08 01:09:19.930035','rejected',685,25,0,0,'unlimited','Remove Bad Images and Resubmit',1,1),(82,'Reasons Why You Should Not Buy Phones For Your Children(Parental Tips)','reasons-why-you-should-not-buy-phones-for-your-childrenparental-tips','<p>strongholdsd is gradually becoming a global village(a global village is a figurative used to express the inter connection of the people in a community via the internet). Today parents see no wrong in getting phones and other electronic devices for their children in a bid to make them happy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today I shall be discussing with you some reasons why you should not buy phones for your children before they turn 18.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;The fact that other people buy phones for their children does not generally give you the impression to get some for yours too,so that they will feel among.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today I shall be enlightening you on some of the dangers of buying phones for your children when they have not come off age.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Lack of concentration in school: From observations,children who have phones and are addicted to it tend to have little interest in anything concerning learning. Even with their friends their core discussions would be what they watched on social media and other unnecessary things.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Exposure to immoral things: The world has become a shadow of the glory our LORD GOD intended it to be. With the high rate of immorality being posted or uploaded on the internet,there is a high chance that your children would become part of such things in terms of viewing or watching them. Especially at the age of puberty when they begin to experience some changes in their body,most children begin to visit these sites to satisfy the new feelings they are developing as a result of puberty.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Bad morals: The truth is that not all children develop this issue but do not totally depend on this because your child could be the victim. When children&nbsp; become too addicted to their phones,they begin to develop some nonchalant attitudes towards everything around them and their responsibilities in the home. They become lazy,easily angered when their phone is tampered with,loose interest in some of the things they loved doing before and so on.<img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t101711960.jpeg\" width=\"640\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Reduced Brain capacity: Apart from the fact that most children who are phone owners are generally less concerned about education, the capacity of their brain is reduced. Now in using a phone,two things are supposed to happen to your brain,one is that your brain capacity is supposed to increase because that phone now serves as a means of making more research downloading live teaching videos from YouTube and also watching other educational programs from the internet. In this way your brain is actually working and being developed. But on the other hand your children might end up totally depending on the internet for virtually all assignment answers. You would begin to notice that they can barely do their assignments on their own without going to the internet. The most embarrassing of all is when they still need the internet to answer questions they are naturally supposed to know. This is one of the negative effects of handling a phone at a tender age. Instead make them do the assignments by themselves,even if they fail it would be an added advantage for them to learn the right method other than getting a pass for what you do not understand. It is better to fail and seek the right method in that way you will be determined to know the right way of doing it other than being comfortable in their ignorance.<img alt=\"\" height=\"320\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t101733299.jpeg\" width=\"480\" /></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>But what happens when you have already bought a phone for your children and you are reading this post? Well being that you have already bought it,this is what you should do;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Time their activities with their phones: give them a specific time limit which they have to operate their devices after which you collect it and hide it in order for them to have time for their books.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Completely seize their phones during tests and exams: Whenever they have a test or exam completely seize their phones for the entire period of the exam.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>As a parent,best time to buy phone or phones for your child is after their senior secondary school certificate examination known as WAEC(this is for countries in West Africa). At that age they are inbtween the veil of adulthood and childhood,so that is when they can be given phones because that sense of control would be in them,because they are now adults. But given a child a phone at his tender age is as good as giving a goat a yam and ordering it not to eat the yam. Please let us endeavor to teach our children the morals our fathers taught us when we were much younger.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The above are the two sure ways I would strongly recommend you to follow if you have already bought phones for your children.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T101711.960.jpeg','2021-03-07 15:52:54.226761','2021-03-07 15:52:54.226812','2021-03-11 19:17:48.690082','rejected',677,18,0,0,'unlimited','Grammatical and spelling errors in the content. Revise and resubmit',1,1),(83,'Five things you should never do in a rush','five-things-you-should-never-do-in-a-rush','<p>In life there are things we all need to know in other to avoid making mistake in our daily life. In this article I will be telling you things you need to know before making big decision in a Rush.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/post_images/Shay_blog/2021/03/07/colorful-heart-candies-and-polaroid-personal-valentines-day-photo-poster_6JKijMw.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Falling in love: most people today go into relationship and they all end up regretting it feeling sad and all, why because they loved the wrong person, they got lust they never loved the right people and for that they end up being in love with the wrong person. You know to be in love with someone is very sweet and amazing, you get to have someone to share your moment with but it feels bad when you lose that person so I think if you want to love make sure you go for the right people but not in a rush.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Making big decisions: you see before you make a decision you need to seek advice from an elderly person. Although there are decision you can take within yourself and it may work out as planned for you but take note not all decision fall in place as planned. For example dropping out of school to go into the labour market to make money because you feel school would waste your time or so but the thing is before taking this kind of decision consult someone older than you someone with experience , your mentor e.t.c so you can be able to understand the kind of path you want to take. Just don&#39;t take big decisions because It worked for Mr A and you think it would work for you that way. You need to plan before taking big decisions so as to succeed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Judging someone&#39;s character: to judge someone&#39;s character or attitude is one of the most important thing we humans should never do in a rush. Sometimes we see someone differently without paying good attention to know more about he or she and for that we give them names, we judge them according to what we see not who they really are. I think it&#39;s really good to understand someone know more about the person before judging them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Give away your trust: to give away your trust or maybe trusting some easily is something most of us regret at the end of the day. Why because we trust the wrong person and maybe we get hurt along the line before getting to know our mistake. We really need to watch closely and know if the person we are giving our trust to really worth it or not. Although most people don&#39;t trust the wrong people it&#39;s just that people change and that&#39;s one of the reason we shouldn&#39;t give away our trust so easily or in a rush.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Eat your own food: I don&#39;t know put this I know it&#39;s really funny but I don&#39;t think it is cool to eat your own food in a rush. The thing that the food is yours it&#39;s going nowhere so I don&#39;t think there is any reason for you to eat your own food in a rush.</p>','','pics/Black_Shape_Photography_Quote.jpg','2021-03-07 17:24:07.470885','2021-03-07 17:24:07.470934','2021-03-12 13:23:14.352028','rejected',679,9,0,0,'unlimited','Article not up to 800 words as stated in the reviewed guideline, significant amount of plagiarism detected.',0,1),(84,'Major Causes Of Depression And Its Solutions','major-causes-of-depression-and-its-solutions','<p>The word depression is a medical condition in which a person feels very sad and anxious often has physical symptoms such as being unable to sleep and so on. In other words, depression is a state of mind whereby an individual is mentally, physically, and emotionally suppressed by negative actions or thoughts. So, before we look into the remedies of depression let us gain a little knowledge about its causes, occurrence, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Everyone gets depressed at some point or stage in life, depression is actually what forms part of our beings as human beings, but as the saying goes <strong>&quot;too much of everything is not good&quot;</strong> this also applies to depression. So we shall briefly be looking at some of the causes of depression.<img alt=\"\" height=\"441\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t182106806.jpeg\" width=\"696\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What are the causes of depression?</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Body shaming:</strong> Body shaming is the act of mocking or making fun of someone due to certain features in their body, or sometimes just laughing at them for the fun of it. Many individuals especially students and the younger generation are fond of this particular crime or act especially to their mates. There have been thousands of cases where children are known to be sadists as a result of body shaming. Let me throw more light into this using this example: There are two students in a classroom, student A and student B, Student A has a deformity in his arm and as a result of this, he is always being mocked and laughed at. This usually makes student A suffer emotional trauma and pain. This is one of the causes of depression in individuals today.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Insulting Words:</strong> One of the most known reasons for depression around the world is the use of insulting words on people. Personally speaking from experience I have seen and been a witness to people who got emotionally depressed as a result of insulting words. In one of such cases, a student playfully called her friend a &#39;snitch&#39;. She never knew her friend got really annoyed and talked less for the rest of the day. <img alt=\"\" height=\"219\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t182410291.jpeg\" width=\"320\" />It was really saddening for her and she later got the hang of it after a lot of comforting words were delivered to her by some friends. This is to tell you that the tongue can cause a lot of damage to an individual&#39;s emotions which would definitely lead to depression.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Lack of achievement of goals: </strong>when we fail to achieve the goals or standards we set for ourselves, it is usually very annoying, frustrating, and depressing. Failure can lead to a great extent of depression, as a matter of fact, it is one of the major causes of depression in the world today. Just visualize a man who planned or intended on building a house before the year runs out and was not able to achieve that task, he or she would both be mentally and physically pained and depressed. I on a more personal note have run into series of depression as a result of non-accomplishments&nbsp;of goals set by myself which I know that I can achieve. A very popular man of GOD once said &quot;the force that pulls you back is the same force that will push you forward&quot;. Many believe that depression is a foul spirit from the kingdom of darkness, but I believed that depression is the avenue for the devil to take advantage of weakness. Because anybody who is suffering from depression is down both physically, mentally, emotionally and in severe cases spiritually. So being that you are now weak, they seize that as an opportunity to plant masty ideas such as suicide into your mind.<img alt=\"\" height=\"452\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t182310456.jpeg\" width=\"678\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Failure:</strong> The feeling of failure is one of the biggest causes of depression in the entire human race. It could be a failure to yourself or a specified task or your loved ones and so on. When you see your classmates (your seatmate in school to be precise) and you mistakenly see him on the television making waves all over the world and you are still struggling to get into the university how do you feel? At this juncture depression sites in, you begin to see yourself as a failure, but the biggest mistake you can make is to listen to the lies that boil in your heart at that very moment when you feel depressed.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The above are some of the known causes of depression all over the world. But there is a little secret I want to share with you, a popular proverb goes <strong>&quot;whatever has an advantage also has a corresponding disadvantage&quot;</strong> this also applies in the opposite direction. When you recover from depression you naturally become stronger than you were before, wiser than you were before, and smarter than you were before. Heartbreak can cause depression but when you recover from heartbreak, you become even wiser than you were before. This generally concords to Newton&#39;s third law of motion which states that &#39;to every action, there is an equal and opposite reaction&#39;. I encourage us all to live the best life. Do not be weighed down by the words, thoughts, and opinions of men, you are the best inspiration you can give yourself. Our Lord Jesus is the best Hope you can give yourself.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T182106.806.jpeg','2021-03-07 17:39:18.487001','2021-03-07 17:39:18.487065','2021-03-11 19:33:20.785339','rejected',677,27,0,0,'unlimited','Solution to depression not stated as promised in the headline, Make article tone non-religious, revise and resubmit.',1,1),(85,'4 Proven Ways To Overcome The Trauma Of Break Up And Divorce','4-proven-ways-to-overcome-the-trauma-of-break-up-and-divorce','<p>There are many broken marriages and relationships all over the world. Many individuals have vowed never to engage themselves in any form of relationship as a result of the heartbreak&nbsp;caused by their former partners, others who cannot bear such pain are tempted to take their own lives. This article&nbsp;is aimed at disclosing&nbsp;ways in which an individual can handle break&nbsp;up.<img alt=\"an arguing couple about to break up\" height=\"480\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t181831990.jpeg\" width=\"640\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to get over a breakup</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most dangerous effects of break up in an individual is depression. Depression is the state of being physically and mentally imbalanced as a result of sad and disturbing past or future events. In every relationship, one of the early signs of imbalance is depression. Depression makes you believe you would never fall in love again, depression makes you hate the person you once loved with so much passion, the final stage of depression is death. So what are some of the things you need to do as an individual to avoid these unpleasant torments caused by break up?</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Don&#39;t beg unless you are wrong:</strong>&nbsp;At that moment when your partner demands a breakup, one of the biggest mistakes individuals make is to beg for the relationship to continue. You are not supposed to beg unless you know you are the one&nbsp;at fault. Sometimes when you apologize and your spouse still demands a breakup, give it to him or her but try not to show any emotions while they are still around. This is because, no matter how deep you love the person, when you cry and beg it makes your vulnerability well known to them. Just accept the breakup and move on with your life, if he or she truly loves you, they would&nbsp;come back.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Avoid memory sparkers:</strong> By memory sparkers, I refer to those things or activities that when you partake in would remind you of your ex-partner. It could be that when you guys were still together you both love&nbsp;visiting the beach, it would do you a whole lot of good to avoid the beach in other to escape the backlashing of memories which would end up in depression. When you take part in such activities they would constantly remind you of the past and give you negative thoughts and ideas that could make you end up making rash decisions. Instead, try out new activities, get engaged with new events, people, and places. If you are financially stable, it would be best considerable you leave that entire geographical entity and start up a new life elsewhere.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>Learn from your mistakes</strong>: First break-ups are usually the most painful and emotional setback an individual can face in life. But the truth is that after such breakups a lot of lessons can be learned by the individual. In life, everything is a lesson, even the air we breathe is teaching us a lesson. So too we must learn from every heartbreak, know our faults in our first relationship and amend&nbsp;them when you finally get into a second relationship, you would be able to stick to your new partner.<img alt=\"heartbroken couples\" height=\"183\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t181736802.jpeg\" width=\"275\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\"><strong>The bridge stage:</strong> I personally introduced this point which I refer to as a bridge point. In some break-ups, despite ending the relationship they continue being friends, while in others they end up being the worst of enemies as they are both overshadowed by pain, anger, and grief. Now, this is why I consider this to be a bridge because some people do not know whether to continue calling their ex-partners in other that they continue as friends or to just totally delete their contacts from their phones. I personally would advise you to go for the one that will best suit you. If you feel that both of you can continue as friends then you do not have a problem, but if you feel the other way around then you can also do as you please.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"girl crying after breakup\" height=\"415\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t181647649.jpeg\" width=\"738\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this, I can confidently draw a close to this article. Always remember that the things that pull us backward are the same things that will push us forward in life. No matter how deep you loved the individual or person, you should not take your life because he left you, do not become drunk and miserable because she dumped you, instead seek revenge, do not even beg for a second chance but seek revenge, revenge in success. Because success is the best revenge you can offer all your haters.</p>','breakup, relationship','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T181831.990.jpeg','2021-03-07 17:45:53.037634','2021-03-07 17:45:53.037682','2021-03-11 19:56:31.267482','published',677,30,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(86,'3 Websites That Will Pay You Real Money To Write For Them','3-websites-that-will-pay-you-real-money-to-write-for-them','<p>Hello there opportunity seeker,today I have outlined and explained a list of 5 websites that pay you real cash to work for words a So what are you waiting for,smash that follow button and sign up with this page to get updated when next we upload such articles. Since the corona virus pandemic ravaged the world,many people lost their jobs and so many were left jobless and had to look for jobs both in the environment around them and on the Internet, well if you are among this set of people today is your lucky day because you are about to make a lot of money if only you read carefully and ask questions in the comments section below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now basically the websites I am going to be showing you are freelancing sites,so what does freelancing mean? It&nbsp; basically means that you would be employed to write for such sites and get paid per the number if articles you publish for thise sites. So if you are skilled in writing,this is an opportunity for you to earn big with your phone or personal computer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Opera News: <img alt=\"\" height=\"415\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t183000495.jpeg\" width=\"739\" />This is one of the most recognized freelancing sites in the world today. Opera news is a news platform set up by opera mini. Yes,the opera mini browser you have on your phone. If you are observant,and a frequent user of the opera mini browser you would notice that in the current versi