to-get-1000-subscribers-on-youtube-within-a-short-period-of-time','<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"368\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t081334089_rDS6Qgl.jpeg\" width=\"668\" />The dream of every youtuber us to get enough traffic and get monetized in other to start earning big on the platform. But as the saying goes &quot;nothing good comes easy&quot; YouTube just like every other money making platforms involves a lot of patience,hardworking and determination in other to meet the platforms criteria which includes getting a total of 1000 active subscribers and a total of 4000 watch hours. Now in this article I would be explaining to you two major ways in which people get or meet this criteria in a very short period of time. I would love it if you click on the follow button to get updated when next I post because my next piece would be on how to earn big on YouTube without having to be a part of your videos,amazing right? So do not hesitate to smash the follow button which us just below this article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So back to our discussion,how to get 1000 subscribers on YouTube,now I shall be revealing to you one of the biggest &#39;cheats&#39; people use to meet this criteria within a space of 7 days or even less. So to do this you need a Facebook account,then search for YouTube subscriber groups in the search bar on Facebook and you will be amazed at the amount of Facebook groups that will pop up,at this juncture apply for membership in as many as you can. Just follow these procedures I shall explain later in this article what you are yo do in this groups, also search for &quot;YouTube sub for sub groups&quot; on Facebook and you will see a whole lot of these groups on facebook,also apply for membership in as many as you can.<img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210305-194243.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>So what does all these languages mean,sub for sub is an abbreviation for subscribers for subscribers