video is all about &quot;how to make money online&quot; you could just include &quot;in my next video I shall be revealing to you 3 sites where you can earn $100 dollars with your phones, so do ensure to click on the subscribe button to get notified when I make the video&quot; and do ensure you make research and post those sites in your next video,this would basically make them click on that button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These among many others are one of the useful tips on how to gain 1000 active subscribers on YouTube. But the truth is that of the two criterias,getting 1000 subscribers is by far the easiest as compared to getting 4000 hours of watch time. But,there are two major ways of meeting this criteria:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Posting videos regularly</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Posting long videos.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The reason I differentiated them into two is because some people are not too good in posting long videos,so if you eventually belong to that set of people the you need to post more often. But if you are a fan of long videos then you can continue in that shade because that is advisably the best way yo meet that criteria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At this juncture I would like to ask you a simple question,do I deserve a thumbs up? If yes do not he state to smash the like button just below this article in other to get updated when next I post. Thank you.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T081334.089.jpeg','2021-03-07 18:08:44.180054','2021-03-07 18:08:44.180105','2021-03-12 13:25:21.091569','rejected',677,11,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guidelines. Refer to the editorial tab on your dashboard',0,1),(88,'How To Earn Money On YouTube (Beginners Tips)','how-to-earn-money-on-youtube-beginners-tips','<p>Being a successful youtuber is not quite easy but as the time passes you would get used to it and understand most of the tricks involved in becoming a well known and renowned youtuber. So basically every youtubers dream is to meet their criteria and get monetized and eventually start earning huge sums of money. But it isn&#39;t as easy as you think. Getting monetized on YouTube is one case,earning big is another. So how do we know or increase our earning capabilities on YouTube? These and many more questions I shall be dealing with today in this article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So if you haven&#39;t read my articles on how to get 1000 subscribers then I urge you to click on the follow button just below this article and search them up and read. So just like google,YouTube pays for ads revenue generated by your channel once it has been monetized. So what are ads? The term &#39;ads&#39; is used to denote an abbreviation for the word &#39;advertisement&#39;,what happens is that big organizations, individuals or firms who wish to create more demand and sellers for their product would pay big websites such as google or YouTube to aid them advertise their goods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is one of the reasons why in virtually all sites or even games you see adverts of certain products in the sites or apps. This is done in order to reach potential customers or buyers of such products. Once someone buys that particular product from your site there is a certain percentage of the sales that will be issued to you. This too is how YouTube pays their monetized youtube,once you get monetized you would be allowed to upload or allow advert placements on your videos. Now,the time an individual spends viewing those adverts determine how much percentage would be given to you. On like order social media platforms, YouTube is one of the few that pays their determined users,,all you need is a lot of determination and originality. One of the biggest mistakes people make in regards to YouTube&#39;s monetization policies is that they feel that once you meet up with their criteria that becomes an avenue to earn big,no,it does not work that way. Aside from the fact that you have met their criteria you still have a lot to do in order to increase your income power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you notice most people who earn big time on YouTube have above 500,000 subscribers,this means that they have more audience than a person with 1000 subscribers, so if YouTube was to place the same adverts on both their channels,who do you think will earn more money? The one with the higher audience of course. So,this simply implies that meeting YouTube&#39;s monetization policies and criteria should not be an avenue to start thinking beyond what your channel can provide,instead struggle to get more. When you have achieved 1000, set a goal of achieving 10000 and so on and so forth. As your zeal increases so too your income power increases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another way of making money on YouTube which is very similar to the first in terms of advert placements is by what is known as paid promotions. Unlike the first where we said that YouTube themselves place the adverts in your video coverage,here private companies,individuals,business owners and so on can pay you a sum of money to aid them advertise their goods or products in your channel. In this course I personally love to refer to it as a contract because,if after you have made the advert in your channel and it yields positive results, the company or individual will pay you to do more.<img alt=\"\" height=\"286\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t181535639.jpeg\" width=\"587\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is one of the reasons why I am emphasising on increasing your subscribers and not solely and tirelessly waiting to cross the 1000 subscriber chain in order to get monetised. Because the higher your subscribers,the higher the chance the paid promotions on your channels,but the lower the subscribers the less the chance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So as an upcoming youtuber,I will urge you to take your time and do not rush into things,allow the process to surpass itself one step at a time. Getting monetised on YouTube is generally not the problem, the real question is not have you monetized? It is how much have you earned since you monetised?<img alt=\"\" height=\"454\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t095536620_SSER6GS.jpeg\" width=\"675\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have seen numerous posts of people who want to sell their monetised YouTube channels for small amounts. And most times I see this,I usually feel as though getting monetised is not the only ball to play if not why are they selling their channel after months of waiting to be monetised?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please click on this follow button just below this article in order to get updated when next I post. Also do not forget to register with us at moreme.com in other to get notified when next an important pistcis both</p>','youtube,monetization,subscribers','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T181535.639.jpeg','2021-03-07 18:15:41.536449','2021-03-07 18:15:41.536500','2021-03-07 18:15:41.536517','pending',677,11,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,0),(89,'Business Tips And Advise On Business Capital Set Up','business-tips-and-advise-on-business-capital-set-up','<p>The rate of unemployment in Nigeria is no longer a topic of interest&nbsp; amongst people. But rather than blaming the government on every occasion, I would be teaching us how to start up a business with very little capital and watch it grow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now for the sake of clarity,a capital is that money or goods which you use to start up a business. You can start a pure water business by purchasing one bag for N100,now that N100 is your capital,because it is the money you invested into the business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now before starting up a business there are certain factors you need to consider before you proceed in your decisions to start up a business,some of them includes;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Place/Location</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The place where your business would be situated is a great determinant of the profits you would make at the end of the day. When you are a pharmacist but situate your shop close to a refuse dump area or site,you would receive less profit just because of the site or location of the business. Always situate your businesses in places or conditions suitable for the expansion of your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What to do</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who are financially backed up and ready to work are sometimes faced with the challenges of not knowing which business to start up. Now there are diverse methods of determining what to start-up when you are stranded.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Knowing what works for you; some people start up little businesses because they are skilled in such areas so therefore setting up a business in relation to their skill will definitely not be a problem.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Scarcity; one of the fastest ways of starting up a&nbsp; business is by knowing what is scarce or rare in the surrounding. When rice is scarce in an area and an individual buys rice for sales in that area,he or she would experience a huge turn out of sales because he is selling a rare or scarce commodity.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Hand work: The truth is that not everyone is cut out to do business,many people can not afford sitting in a shop and awaiting customers,so they turn their gifts or hand works into money making engines. Instead of waiting for an oil company job,you can start earning from the comfort of your home,all you need is to put your mind into what you are doing to grow your talent. If you can sew or into bead making and the rest,these are hand works that can earn you lots of money.<img alt=\"\" height=\"435\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t095346878.jpeg\" width=\"705\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Loan: I personally cannot advise people to take loans,but if you are sure of repayment then do not hesitate to sign up a loan form in the bank. There are many people who have the ideas of what to do,they are generally vision and goal oriented but their only problem is that they do not have the sufficient funds to start up their plans. If you happen to be a part of this group of people then you should not hesitate to take a loan from the bank because I believe that whatever a man chases with pure intentions,he must succeed.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Hiring and dismissal of clients or employee&#39;s: One of the most painful decisions you can make as a business owner who is struggling in business is to dismiss your employees. But if you notice a backslide in business then you can let go of some employees.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">Internet wise: Today there are many online jobs people engage themselves in, in order to earn a living,some of them include YouTube, freelancing,networking,marketing affiliation and so on. In order words you do not necessarily need your certificate in order to apply for most of the inline jobs,all you need is an active data connection and you are good to go.<img alt=\"\" height=\"415\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t095438703.jpeg\" width=\"739\" /> As a matter of fact,the internet has become one of the biggest platforms for job acquisitions all you need to do is to search for what fits you. But in whatever you do, never participate in online fraud, always try to be genuine in whatever you do.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>These are some of the factors in considering the type of business you want to set up. From my experience,I feel that the most important thing a person needs before setting up a business us GOD,because without His direction we are mere scalar quantities. Laziness brings room for different immoral thoughts, it is through laziness and idleness that the thought of kidnapping,ritual killings,theft and so on. So it is good to always engage yourself in something that will not only keep you busy but earn you money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please do ensure to click on the follow button to get updated when next I post and do not hesitate to register to this website to get updated on articles and life tips that will add morals to your life. Thank you.</p>','money,business,capital','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T095438.703.jpeg','2021-03-07 18:27:17.848871','2021-03-07 18:27:17.848945','2021-03-07 18:27:17.848976','pending',677,17,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,0),(90,'5 Crucial Things You Should Never Do In Front Of Your Children(Parenting Tips)','5-crucial-things-you-should-never-do-in-front-of-your-childrenparenting-tips','<p>Being a parent is not an easy task, but the truth can never be overemphasized. What you implant in your children when they are young is what they will become when they age.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gone are the days when children had regards for their parents and instructions from older people. Today, their main course of worry is owning an expensive smartphone, wristwatch and other lists of irrelevant materials. The bitter truth behind all this is that sometimes the parents play a huge role in the deformation of a child&#39;s character. In this article, I shall be discussing some of the things parents do that alter the mental, physical education and physiological outputs of children.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Using Vogue/Insulting words on them: Many parents are fond of this, whenever a child does something wrong they end up insulting him or her, but you forget that they are still tender and will easily learn or grab whatsoever you throw at them be it good or bad. Writing from experience, I was once a witness to a scene where a father used the &#39;f&#39; word on his son who is still in elementary school. How do you think this boy will grow? There is a saying that goes &quot; you become what you hear &quot; when you continuously tell your child that he is a goat and he suddenly starts loving grass you have yourself to blame. Aside from the joke, we must say nice words to our children, no matter how angry they make us. Always remember that you are grooming them for the betterment of the world tomorrow.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Beating your spouse in front of your children: One of the major courses of emotional trauma in children is as a result of what they observe in the home. When you beat or quarrel with your wife in front of your children, how do you expect them to cope with the rest of the day after witnessing what you have done? In some cases, some children also grow to become like their parents because the home they are coming from is unstable.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Making love in front of your children: The truth is that the current generation of children seems to be by far the worst in terms of exposure to many things they are not supposed to know. When you are fond of making love with your partner in front of your children how do you expect them to behave when they go to school and meet other genders? Yes, of course, they will want to practice what they saw you doing. This is why it is very important to navigate the potential in the right direction and not in the oath of evil.<img alt=\"\" height=\"401\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t194546178.jpeg\" width=\"765\" /></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Comparisons: There are lots of thoughts and considerations as to how comparisons between children aid their development. Now, what does comparison mean? In general notation, a comparison is an act of making a better choice out of two more choices. Many parents are fond of comparing their children with the children of other people, they would be like &quot;don&#39;t you see how obedient Jessica is?&quot; And so many more, yes we see how obedient she is but can you see the dark parts of her life? In my opinion, I feel parents should stop comparing their children with other people&#39;s children because you can never tell what they face even with that child you see as a blessing. Always be grateful to GOD for giving you the children you have. If you feel they are growing in a way that is not pleasing to GOD you can always spare the rod and spoil the child.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Insult or make fun of other people: One of the most vital things you should flee from as a parent is insulting either your children or outsiders&#39;. The first point dealt with insults directed at the children but this last point needs to be treated with all carefulness. <img alt=\"\" height=\"414\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t194523074.jpeg\" width=\"740\" />Avoid the use of nasty languages with your spouse, friends, etc when your children are around. This can greatly affect their future. A man was fond of calling his best friend a fool(although it was in form of a joke) but each time he did this his little daughter was always observant and tried as much as she could to understand what they were always discussing because she was tender, about 5 years old. One fateful day, as this man drove his daughter to school, she sighted her dad&#39;s best friend. Since she did not know his name, she stood from the car window and shouted &quot;Fool&quot; to the amazement of everyone(fiction).&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>So was this girl wrong in calling that young man a fool? No of course! because that&#39;s how she had been brought up.<img alt=\"\" height=\"473\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/07/images-2021-03-07t194459175.jpeg\" width=\"648\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In conclusion, you can breed your household in the right direction by teaching them to pray and read the word of GOD alongside other educational and spirit building books other than the above mentioned. Where you come from can partially determine who you would be.</p>','parenting','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T194523.074.jpeg','2021-03-07 18:53:06.616281','2021-03-07 18:53:06.616343','2021-03-07 22:52:29.124939','published',677,18,1,1,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(91,'Milan Fashion Week Opened by African designers.','milan-fashion-week-opened-by-african-designers','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"Huhttps://www.instagram.com/tv/CMA7IObDJKL/?igshid=1ghvdac83cwjh\" />Five Africa-born designer have opened the Milan fashion week, a first for Italy&#39;s most Prestigious couture show.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"248\" src=\"/media/post_images/Alex_oche/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210226-1752383.png\" width=\"382\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Michelle Ngonmo, the co-founder of the collective Made in Italy, called the event, which was recorded in advance as a result of the pandemic, a first step towards a more equal society. The most prominent fashion weeks are held in the fashion capital of the world such as; Paris, Milan, London and Newyork, which receives the majority of press coverage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"587\" src=\"/media/post_images/Alex_oche/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210226-1809103.png\" width=\"395\" />&nbsp;Michelle Ngonmo acknowledged the debt owed to the black lives matter movement, but said the five designers she had chosen had demonstrated that the Made in Italy label was not a question of racism but of technical know-how. Thanks to a movement highlighting racism in the fashion industry, five designers of African origin led the We are Made in Italy runway show. Who are they?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The five, Fabiola Manirakiza from Burundi, Claudia Gisele Ntsama from Cameroon, the Senegalese Mokodu Fall, Joy Meribe of Nigeria and Moroccan Karim Daoudi, all learnt some of their skills in Africa but are now naturalised Italian citizens. The show is the result of a collaboration between the National chamber of Italian fashion and the black lives matter in Italian fashion movement. Last year, Italian-Haitian designer Stella Jean, Milan-based African American designer, Edward Buchanan and Afro fashion week Milano founder Michelle Ngonmo, were the one&#39;s who stated the movement to highlight racism in the fashion industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The designers showed five looks on the runway, with the most of the Milan fashion week show taking place online this year as a result of the corona virus pandemic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The visual show aim to support black creators by giving a platform to designers with diverse background.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Milan is one of the popular world fashion capital. Prominent features like Prada, Jil Sander, Gucci, Armani, Fendi, Bottega Veneta, Etro, Marni, Versace, Missoni and Salvatore Ferragamo are just a few who will host their show at Milan fashion week. Previously, the presentation of the collections of black designers was confined to Afro fashion week, which was launched in Milan with a show in 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many of the Africa-born designers moved to Italy at a young age. They faced considerable obstacles on their road to recognition, with some working in low-pay jobs to finance their passion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Born in different part of Africa but operating under the Made in Italy brand, here are the brief history of the five designers who opened Milan fashion week as part of a collective.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Fabiola Manirakiza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She was born in Burundi, but it was in Zaire, which became the Democratic Republic of Congo, that she learned how to sew, in a school run by run by Italian nun. She went to Italy as a child. A doctor by training, she used this skill untill when she founded her label Frida Kiza in Italy in 2016, the name gives a tribute to Mexican artist Frida Kahlo. She describes her design as a mix between Africa and Italy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Claudia Gisele Ntsama.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Born in Cameroon, has since childhood wanted to be a designer and particularly in Italy, as Fashion is Italy. She spent eight years learning Italian before moving to Italy in 2012, where she worked in odd jobs, in cleaning and at a football stadium entrance among others, before getting a diploma in design from Bologna. She fell in love with hemp, one of the most ecological fibres and built her own label.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Mokodu Fall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He is originally from Senegal, he worked as a cartoonist, actor and then painter. He went to Italy at the age of 22 to experience the art and culture. His textiles are hand painted with African-inspired images. His works are work of art that he transpose in clothes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Joy Meribe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She left Nigeria where she was born because there, designers have no status. She is currently 43 years of age. She obtained a masters in international business before entering fashion.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"262\" src=\"/media/post_images/Alex_oche/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210226-1808433.png\" width=\"422\" />She said she is not an ethnic designer, she lived in Italy, studied in Italy and produce in Italy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Karim Daoudi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He born in Morocco 27 years ago, arrived in San Mauro Pascoli in Northern Italy at the age of 13 with his family, looking for a better future. At age 17, he started working in workshop making shoes of different brands, before winning a competition on shoe design in Rome. His collection is entitled Journey into the Forest, brings together shoes in bright colours that reminds him of Morocco. To finance his passion, he works as a postman to finance his designer dream.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"248\" src=\"/media/post_images/Alex_oche/2021/03/07/screenshot_20210226-1759473.png\" width=\"255\" /></p>','','pics/Screenshot_20210225-154914.png','2021-03-07 23:59:40.475016','2021-03-07 23:59:40.475085','2021-03-08 01:05:51.968399','rejected',684,1,0,0,'unlimited','Outdated Content(Feb 24), News articles not allowed',0,1),(92,'This Is The Best Remedy To Use If You Want To Loose A Lot Of Fat','this-is-the-best-remedy-to-use-if-you-want-to-loose-a-lot-of-fat','<p>There are many individuals who wish and are desperate to get rid of the fat in their bodies. There are different categories of people in regards to body shapes or types,some are fat,some are chubby, some are slim and so on. But today we shall not be dwelling on the type of the body but the solutions to get a perfect or desirable body shape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being fat is caused by the excessive accumulation of calories in the body.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being fat is not bad at all but due to some certain factors such as excess eating,body shaming and so on,many individuals wish to reduce their body size.&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" height=\"330\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-07t182721454_gQ44Z58.jpeg\" width=\"620\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The truth is that the best and most recommendable way of getting rid of excess fat is by exercising. Exercise helps you burn enough fat and reduce the calorie content of the body thereby leading to loss of weight and reduction in body fat. But how does this work?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now fats are stored in the body as lipids,these lipids or fats can easily dissolve as a result of rise in temperature, so in essence,heat is a major component for the dissociation of fats in the body. When you partake in exercises such as running in the early hours of the morning,you tend to sweat a lot. This is because those exercises are meant to heat up the body so that excess fats can be burned,and when they melt they co.e out as sweat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the major reason why you are advised to exercise till you sweat,because that is when the work has literally begun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By doing so,you are sure to lose a lot of pounds if only you are consistent and persistent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from losing fat, exercise is very vital in general human growth and in keeping a healthy mind and body. For the slim people one of the ways of getting or adding weight is by participating in exercises. Now how is this possible? Let us say that you weigh 85 kilograms presently and you still wish to add more weight,all you need to do is to partake in regular exercises on a daily basis for at least a period of six months. At the end of the site months period check your weight and be amazed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the terrible effects of being excessively fat is heart failure. I am sure you are wondering how being fat can affect your heart. Of course it certainly can and even do a lot more than that. Now when excessive fat piles around your heart there is a high chance of it blocking your arteries which are blood vessels thereby stopping the even flow of blood from your heart to other parts of your body. In some cases thus can lead to consistent heart attacks or heart failures.<img alt=\"\" height=\"415\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-07t182806966_2ep4pTn.jpeg\" width=\"739\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is also important to note that trying to lose weight or reduce body fat by means of drugs or induced features into your body can be highly dangerous. Some people resort to the intake of harmful medicines,the truth is that you certainly would lose a lot of fat but the effects the drugs would have on you generally would be another different story to tell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a single lady who is not yet married,it is very advisable that you engage in exercise in other to reduce fats and calories in your body if you have or possess them in excess. This is because most women tend to increase in size and body mass when they get married and especially after child birth. So if you are literally fat now it would be of great importance to do some work outs now before getting married. One of the major reasons why women are more pressured on the area of losing body fat than men is because of their status and roles in the society which span across child birth,marital and economic responsibilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please if you are fat avoid any drugs or substances that people tell or advise you to take for quicker results, despite the fact that they might work out well,the side effects they impose on the user might be worse than their previous predicaments. Yes,exercising your way out of obesity might take time,but it is more health approved than drugs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To the general public: Exercise is very important to the general public whether you are fat or slim. An average human is expected to exercise at least twice a day every single day. In fact the best time to exercise is in the early hours of the morning between 4am-6am in the morning. This is the time were people take part in road works and other exercises.</p>','','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T182721.454.jpeg','2021-03-08 05:33:56.281568','2021-03-08 05:33:56.281631','2021-03-12 13:33:44.045153','rejected',677,27,0,0,'unlimited','Significant amount of plagiarism found, article not up to 800 words, spelling and grammatical errors found',0,1),(93,'3 proven methods to recover your hacked social media account (Facebook, Twitter, etc)','3-proven-methods-to-recover-your-hacked-social-media-account-facebook-twitter-etc','<p>Insecurity is one of the biggest challenges we face in our world today. This spans physical insecurity, emotional insecurity, and even cyber insecurity. In this article, I&nbsp;shall be dwelling on the latter. But before I begin, let me define the word insecurity to the simplest form possible.&nbsp;Insecurity is the state of not being safe or in safe hands. Cyber insecurity is the feeling of shared privacy with an identified user or hacker.<img alt=\"Image illustration of a social media hacker\" height=\"554\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-07t080036842.jpeg\" width=\"554\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There have been and are still cases of account hacking all over the world. To hack means to invade someone&#39;s privacy unpermitted (without the consent of the owner).</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to know if your account has been hacked</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are diverse ways to know if your account has been hacked but we shall be looking at a few relevant and often recurring ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong>Unknown messages: </strong>When you log into any of your social media accounts and see strange messages that you do not recall sending, then have it at the back of your mind that your privacy has been shared by someone else.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong>Unknown/unusual login:</strong> sometimes you might log out or sign out of your media account only to come back or discover that you are still active, possibly when you are with another person&#39;s phone.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong>Cannot log in:</strong> this is the most popular method used by hackers, when a hacker finds or gains access into your account they change everything about the account including your password and number. So, when next you try to log in it would not be possible because the details of the account have been tampered with.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong>Unusual/unknown posts:</strong> when you log in to your account and you see posts on your profile that you did not send then know that your account has been hacked.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The truth is that most of these hackers need other people&#39;s accounts to promote whatever evil they want to perpetuate with it. Some use people&#39;s accounts to post adult content, others to dupe people, and so on.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a matter of fact, one of the biggest reasons why people hack other people&#39;s social media accounts is to fake their identity to earn the victim&#39;s friend&#39;s trust. On many occasions, I have been frequently asked if I was still using my Facebook account, but knowing full well the intentions of these people I had to show them the red card.&nbsp;<img alt=\"Security illustration \" height=\"423\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-07t080147171_hflxt2Y.jpeg\" width=\"634\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The moment you notice any of the above experiences in any of your social media platforms be it Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram, and so on, you should know that your privacy is being tampered with. One of the best ways of detecting to know if your account has been manipulated&nbsp;is by regularly checking the list of phones you last logged into.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What does this mean?</strong> It means that each time you log in to your social media platform whatever device you used&nbsp;would be saved in your account settings. All you need to do is to go to the &quot;<strong>settings and privacy&quot;</strong>,&nbsp;look for security settings, then you can now check for active devices (this shows the places or phones where your account was&nbsp;previously and are currently logged in).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you see a strange device you never logged your account into, you can try removing the device. Social media like Facebook automatically logs you out of the intruder&#39;s device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also as a social media user, you are supposed to use a very strong password that comprises letters, numbers, and symbols. This makes the password&nbsp;difficult for hackers/intruders to guess. Most times hackers get into their victim&#39;s account by permutating their date of birth, pet names, spouse&#39;s name, etc. This is the core reason why most sites will insist that you include symbols, numbers, and letters before you can fully complete your log-in information on the site. The reason they do this is to aid you to get a strong bridge of privacy in your account. One of the safest sites I do commend is Google, such that when you try or someone tries to access your Gmail with another device aside from the recognized one, a mail will be sent to your phone telling you about a breach of privacy and asking if you were the one that authorized that login, if you say no, then access to your Gmail account will totally be denied on the other device.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to recover a hacked social media account</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The deed has been done, the intruder has gained access into your account, now you are worried about how you can gain full access to your account. If you are able to detect a privacy breach as soon as possible, it is easier to recover your account. However, a privacy breach that has lasted for weeks or months&nbsp;might be irreversible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are few ways to regain access to a hacked account:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Try the password recovery method</strong>: most sites come with a password recovery method, it is a way to recover your account after you&nbsp;forget your log-in details. It also comes in handy when an intruder logs you out of your account. The first thing a hacker does when they gain access to your account is trying to change your password so that you no longer have access to that account. If your recovery information has not been tampered with( probably you discovered the hack earlier), you can recover it by visiting your social media&#39;s <strong>&#39;forgot password&#39;</strong> page.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Have your friends report the account:</strong> once an intruder has your social media account, contact your friends as soon as possible because they might fall victim to the account. Get them to report the account for suspicious acts. The intruder will be denied access to the account then you can file for account recovery.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>File for account recovery:</strong> each social media platform provides a way to contact the help desk whenever anything goes wrong with your account on their platform. You can be asked for a valid means of identification like a voter&#39;s card or utility bill before they can proceed with account recovery.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to recover a hacked Facebook account</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most targeted&nbsp;social media is Facebook.&nbsp;I have seen countless people asking for help on how to recover their hacked Facebook account. You can follow the steps below if you no&nbsp;longer have access to your account.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Use Facebook recovery method:</strong> Facebook comes with a password recovery method to regain access to your account. <a href=\"https://web.facebook.com/login/identify?_rdc=1&amp;_rdr\" target=\"_blank\">Visit Facebook&#39;s password recovery page</a>, search for your account. Then follow the instructions to gain access to your hacked account.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Facebook password recovery page\" height=\"533\" src=\"/media/post_images/Moremegaming/2021/03/12/password_reset.JPG\" width=\"1311\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Have your friend reset it for you via your profile</strong>: tell your friend to visit your wall on Facebook. Tell them to locate the <strong>&quot;...&quot; </strong>button below your cover photo. They should select &quot;find support or report profile&quot;. Tell them to click on &quot;something else&quot;, followed by &quot;recover this account&quot;. They should follow all the instructions stated after the prompt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If these two methods aren&#39;t working or your issue wasn&#39;t described in this article<a href=\"https://web.facebook.com/help/1306725409382822\" target=\"_blank\">, You should contact the Facebook help desk.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hackers don&#39;t have access to an account by magic, most times you give out your information unknowingly. Always avoid clicking on spammy links, logging your account details on an unrecognized site. Most of the time these sites disguise as a money-making website just to get access to your account. Finally, do not share sensitive details with strangers on social media, always learn to use your <strong>block </strong>button.</p>','hack, facebook, twitter','pics/images_-_2021-03-07T080036.842.jpeg','2021-03-08 05:52:06.074041','2021-03-08 05:52:06.074091','2021-03-12 19:00:03.070486','published',677,1,1,1,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(94,'Students: Reasons Why You Should Never Disrespect Your Academic Tutors','students-reasons-why-you-should-never-disrespect-your-academic-tutors','<p>Their are many nasty things students do to annoy,or make fun of their tutors but today we shall be discussing but a few and giving you reasons why you as a student should desist from such acts. So please I urge you to click on the follow button to get updated when next I make a post.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many students fail courses or subjects not just because the lecturer or teacher wants to portray evil on them but sometimes as result of the behavioral outputs of such students. You result span across character and understanding. <img alt=\"\" height=\"225\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-08t065549575.jpeg\" width=\"225\" />Below are some of the things you as a student should not do to your tutors;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Mock them: Many teachers have been badly mocked or mimicked by students either because of their dressing, or manner if talking and so on. You should always know that these same teachers are Human beings like you who have feelings like you do. Mocking your teachers only make them loose the interest they have in teaching you.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Refusal to do take home assignment: Some students exhibit nonchalant attitudes towards take home assignments,this is a very bad character to exhibit. Now,most students feel as though they are being hard on their teachers when ever they refuse to do assignments but they are far from the truth. Your teachers are the ones who dispenses knowledge to you,so if you prove to be a hard but to crack then you will live in your own self imposed ignorance.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Playing pranks on teachers: Your teachers are your tutors,no matter how old they are,you most allocate the respect they deserve to them. It is quite unfortunate that students often make jokes of their teachers,forgetting that these are the same people who impacted them with knowledge.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Missing classes: On a more personal opinion, I feel that the highest level of disrespect you can offer any teacher,yourself and your parents is to miss classes. As much as you can never miss a certain teachers class because you feel you do not like the teacher,that is one of the biggest ways of showing disrespect to teachers.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">Criticism: Most students are fond of criticising their teachers when they go wrong or make a little mistake. I on a more personal note have seen cases where students try to bring difficult questions for their teachers to solve or answer,secretly intending that the teacher faulters in their explanation so that they would seize that opportunity to announce to the entire school that the teacher does not know what he or she is doing. This is also very common with students when they are in class,when your teacher makes a little mistake, students begin to laugh or giggle as though they were expecting such to happen. This character needs to be stopped by students because it speaks less of the positive sides of their personalities.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"452\" src=\"/media/post_images/%40Stanley123/2021/03/08/images-2021-03-08t065626452.jpeg\" width=\"678\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These among others are few of many other atrocities you should never try on your teachers. Instead bombard them with questions,strive to know as much as they do,that is why you pay school fees. It does not just end in the classroom it goes beyond that. We should all stop our nonchalant attitudes if we are among these sets of students. Always remember that your teachers are wiser and more experienced than you are in terms of exposure to the outside world and academically,sometimes I feel sad when I see or hear about students who engage in fights with their teachers. Teachers are the bed rock of the society. The best part about being a human being is that you never stop learning,so no matter the level you find yourself always remember that your have taught and been taught both voluntarily and involuntarily.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One thing students fail to understand is that the best repayment you can give to your teacher is success,they do not necessarily need your money,all they need is to see you succeed. Many students and schools all over the world appreciate their teachers for a hib well done. But the truth if the whole issue is that the profession that is supposed to be respected the most amongst others is being neglected. One of the best set of teachers I personally appreciate the most are the teachers or kindergarten/play class and nursery one or grade one teachers. For a person to input knowledge into the skull of a baby who knows nothing other than &#39;daddy&#39;,&#39;money&#39;,biscuit&#39; and so on is simply beautiful and unimaginable. So we are supposed to be greatful to GOD for our teachers,because if not for them,you will not have read this far into this article and there will be no need to write an article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please click on the follow button to get updated when next I post,also subscribe to this sites channel so that article updates will be sent directly to you.</p>','education,school,students','pics/images_-_2021-03-08T065549.575.jpeg','2021-03-08 06:03:02.619141','2021-03-08 06:03:02.619190','2021-03-08 06:03:02.619206','pending',677,9,0,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,0),(96,'What You Need To Know About Becoming A Vegetarian','what-you-need-to-know-about-becoming-a-vegetarian','<p>We live in a world where people choose a particular way of life that suits them. They make choices to match their various lifestyles.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to what people choose when it comes to the type of meals they consume, some fall in the meat-eating category while others are strictly vegetables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"A smiling vegetarian in the kitchen\" height=\"459\" src=\"/media/post_images/Goldy/2021/03/08/img_20210308_145544.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vegetarianism has recently gained popularity in the course of trying to eat healthily. Healthy living is what all belief is being in shape and fit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The questions that come to mind are;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is vegetarianism?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who is a vegetarian?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Are there types of vegetarians?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Is being a vegetarian good for me?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What meals can I eat as a vegetarian?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What meals can I eat as a vegetarian on a budget?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Preparing vegetable and meals for vegetarians\" height=\"475\" src=\"/media/post_images/Goldy/2021/03/08/img_20210308_145530.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What is vegetarianism?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>One might wonder if this word actually exists. True, it does and this is what it means in simple terms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vegetarianism is described as the act of not eating or consuming animal products, in which we know meat is largely involved.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This might sound absurd. How can I survive without eating meat?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This answers the question &quot;<strong>what can I eat as a vegetarian?</strong>&quot; This will be answered in the later parts of this article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vegetarians are individuals that don&#39;t have meat nor consume its products. They take lots of vegetables, fruits, grains, and proteins from plant sources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The definition actually sounds boring, but does this mean I have to eat vegetables all day?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This question has been answered below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are there types of vegetarians?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This might sound like a sigh of relief. There are many types of vegetarians which might fit your intended lifestyle. These are discussed below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Lacto vegetarian:</strong> These types of vegetarians have plant-based food such as fish and eggs, dairy products. These do not include fish and eggs or poultry products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Ovo vegetarians:</strong> People under this category, consume plant-based food, dairy products, and eggs except for meat, fish, and poultry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Lacto-Ovo vegetarians: </strong>They eat plant-based food, dairy products, and eggs excluding meat, poultry, and fish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Pesco vegetarians:</strong> This bracket of vegetarians, eat fish but rarely meat.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The above-listed types of vegetarians show that becoming a vegetarian is not so hard. It just needs a little bit of discipline and consistency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First, we need to understand that being a vegetarian is a choice and it&#39;s no big deal if you decide to become one.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Is being a vegetarian good for me?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This question is answered based on what the individual wants in the question.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Can I keep up with the rules of becoming one?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The answer is simple. On the bright side, being a vegetarian is a good choice for you. It is healthy and keeps the organs working in good condition. If you notice, they hardly fall sick because they get the right nutrients in the right proportion.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This does not mean that non-vegetarians are not healthy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What meals can I have as a vegetarian?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The meals to take solely&nbsp;depend&nbsp;on the type of vegetarian you decide to be. Stricter vegetarians have meals from more plant sources than others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can decide to draw up a menu for the family or how you can manage your newfound lifestyle.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What meals can I have as a vegetarian on a budget?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This question is better answered based on your income capacity, hence the budget mentioned.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can decide to choose from meals that are pocket-friendly which will help you save enough for other emergencies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You can have any of these meals;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Legumes and vegetables:</strong> Legumes include beans, peas, and grains rich in protein. A combination of any of these with a good quantity of vegetables will do the job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Vegetable burgers:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>This is for those who love burgers but want to be vegetarians too. You can substitute the meat content for a suitable vegetable that suits you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Fried rice:</strong> This is one meal that can be easily prepared in a few minutes and will make a good choice on the menu too.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Pasta and vegetable sauce:</strong> Pasta lovers, this is for you. You can always enjoy your pasta with any vegetable of your choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Vegetable sauce and white rice:</strong> This is also not a bad idea too when it comes to what can be consumed with white rice. This dish is also a good option to try out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These meals are only suggestions which you can decide to make to have as a vegetarian on a budget.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also decide to explore recipes and see what goes best for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The decision to become a vegetarian is one of the best things you can ever think of, it does not only keep you in shape but you get to explore various food nutrients made available by nature.</p>','#lifestyle #vegetarian','pics/IMG_20210308_145530.jpg','2021-03-08 15:07:35.198530','2021-03-08 15:07:35.198576','2021-03-08 18:01:19.113560','published',669,21,1,0,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1),(99,'Meet These Celebrities Who Went From \'Grass To Grace\' That Has Inspired Me To Work Hard.','meet-these-celebrities-who-went-from-grass-to-grace-that-has-inspired-me-to-work-hard','<p>We have many celebrities of the world who went through hell before becoming who they are today. These celebrities include men and women who have stood the test of time in achieving what they have today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Wizkid.<img alt=\"\" height=\"697\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/08/screenshot_20210308-1903322.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wizkid is a popular Nigerian singer and songwriter who had noting when he started making music in Lagos state. Wizkid had the passion and talent for singing so this has kept him going for over these years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wizkid really struggle to become where he is today as he disclosed it in his song titled &#39;Ojuelegba&#39;. This song was a summary of &nbsp;his life, how he stared recording songs in &#39;Modox studios&#39; while tutored by Banky W.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He is one of the biggest Afro pop singer in Africa who has gained recognition worldwide. He&#39;s wonderful singing style has made him win numerous awards like; the Headies award and Grammy nominations for the best artiste of the year in Africa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One thing in love with Wizkid is that his love and passion for music will never die, because he gives us good vibes and lyrics which makes meaning and this is what has made his fans love him and promoted his music career since 2010. If you listen to his latest album &#39;Made in Lagos&#39; you will hear good tracks which will make you feel awesome. Some of these tracks include; Blessed, True love, Gyrate, Grace and Essence which he featured Tems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The singer through hardworking and determination has earned millions of dollars from singing, and has endorsement deals from many companies since day one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Zlatan.<img alt=\"\" height=\"733\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/08/screenshot_20210308-1904532.png\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zlatan is a popular Nigerian singer and rapper who gained recognition for his singing style in Youruba dialect. The singer was also a street boy who struggled to become who he is today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He became popular after he released a hit song titled &#39;Zanku&#39; few years back. The song also has it&#39;s dance which he formed with Poco Lee the afro dancer. Since then, Zlatan has worked hard to improve his music career as his fans loved his music and expected more from him.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nigerian youths loved Zlatan because his rapping style was good, the beats he used were danceable. As an artist who would want to develop himself, he featured other big celebrity singers who were already in the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zlatan who was an ordinary street boy is now a big artist in Nigeria as his net worth runs in thousands of dollars. He own various luxurious cars. furthermore, he has his own mansion in Lagos state which worth millions of Naira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Olamide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"889\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/08/fb_img_16077067262913986.jpg\" width=\"720\" />Olamide has also being producing music for a long time now. Back then when he was less financial equipped, he struggled to promote his music career but this did not stop him from fulfilling his long time dream of becoming a popular artiste.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Olamide just like Zlatan is a street Yoruba rapper right from time. Olamide improved his rapping skills to become who he is today. On my opinion, Nigerians love him and his ghetto singing style which makes meaning and passes a strong message.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Olamide is a living testimony for hardwork and passion. He has won several Headies awards and nominations over the past few years he has being active. Olamide who was a street boy loved making music and God has guided him throughout these years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&#39;ll advice you to learn from Olamide&#39;s success story. I want you to know that no good thing in this world comes easy, you just need to grow tougher and hence wiser to achieve your dreams no matter what people say or think about you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Mayorkun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mayorkun is a top notch artist who also went from &#39;grass to grace&#39; before becoming who he is now, and from what am seeing he may grow to become one of the biggest Afro pop singer in Africa and beyond.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The singer struggled for signing and recognition from big record labels so as to advance his career but through hardwork and passion for music, he was finally signed to DMW by Davido in 2016. He was signed the same day with Dremo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since Mayorkun was signed to DMW his life suddenly changed and he has released big hit songs. Some of them which he featured his boss; Davido. Through hardwork and knowledge for good music making, he released a hit song titled &#39;Geng&#39; which won a Headies award for the best street anthem in Nigeria year 2021.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I hope these various artist and there success stories will motivate you to work hard and not relent in what ever good thing your are doing. Rember that hard work pays and he who works harder, gains more.<img alt=\"\" height=\"800\" src=\"/media/post_images/Gist_World/2021/03/08/fb_img_15951024093532871_YVBBCAw.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>','','pics/Screenshot_20210308-1904532.png','2021-03-08 19:56:49.464303','2021-03-08 19:56:49.464428','2021-03-11 19:14:36.141098','rejected',650,2,0,0,'unlimited','Remove the \'x\' marks on images, correct blunders, click to revise and resubmit.',1,1),(101,'How To Become A Better Footballer','how-to-become-a-better-footballer-4497','<p>&nbsp;Football is one of the most popular sports with a following of over three and a half billion people. Wherever you turn, at whichever corner of the world you turn to, you&#39;ll find a pitch, a football, and players. Football players are an integral part of the sport. There are countless players who pride themselves as football players. However, to stand out above the rest and be a world recognized player takes a lot. If you&#39;re wondering if you have what it takes to have the world watch you on the pitch, or you want to grow your skills, here are the top tips on how to become a successful professional football player</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Be on a balanced diet.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a football player, you need to be on perfect balanced diet so as to make you fit and strong to play. Eating protein based food and other classes of food can do the trick. Eat protein based foods like eggs, poultry, full fat dairy products will put u in go shape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Drink plenty of water.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Water is life&quot;, this means we need water to survive, staying hydrated is important for your overall health, especially if you&#39;ve started playing the sports. Drink at least 4 cups (1,900mL) before a match as it gives you energy. Keep in mind, when the weather is hot drink enough water, so as to cover for the excess sweating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Practice a lot.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Practice makes perfect. Practicing what you are good at doesn&#39;t only make you good at it but the best.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. Find a team.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finding a team is one of the most important aspect in becoming a better player. You need to find a team in which you can practice what you are good at. You can choose a team at your local environment or even at the professional level which you can train.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Make friends on the team.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Making friends on your team is really important as it makes you to understand them. In other for you to be successful in your career you need to be able to associate with them, so as to understand the likes and dislikes of your teammates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Know the rules of the game.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowing the rules if the game is also an essential part of football. You have to understand the game and what it&#39;s all about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Have a player&#39;s kit.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can&#39;t go to school without a uniform, as you can&#39;t play ball without a football kit. Example of the football kit are your jersey, boot etc. In getting a football kit, you have to get what fits well, comfortable, and attractive so as to attract viewers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Motivation.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Motivation goes a long way in making great players. Motivation is what keeps you going even when the odds are stacked against you. When you go back to some of the greatest games in history, you&#39;ll realize a fair share were won by sheer motivation. The whole team may have given up, but a player or two still believed they could do it, and true to the testament, they did. Look for something that motivates you and key in on it. Playing in the World Cup, or winning a trophy can be great motivators. Even when you&#39;re playing a game and it&#39;s not going well, when you picture your motivation, you will be energized to give the game your best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9. Get a mentor.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mentors are those people who are in the same field as you are, and you look up to them and aspire to be like them. In football, there are legends that have gone ahead and set records either at local, regional, or international levels.You should scout your area and see if there is anyone who has achieved what you would want to, and see if they would be willing to help you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10. Give your body time to recover.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many football players are prone to injuries. Some are easy to recover from, while others are career ending. This is due to the exhaustive training and exercising that they undergo on a daily basis. When you are hurt, the first instinct may be to brush it off and continue playing. However, when you do that, you will only cost your team and your body. If you suspect you have an injury or something that needs attention, you should alert the coach, and have a trained medic have a look. When you are fully recovered, you will have your chance on the field. Also, it is important to give your body resting days to help it cope with the regular training and exercising.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>11. Appreciate the place of patient.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As mentioned earlier, while setting goals, you need to be realistic. One of the skills that can help you become a successful professional footballer is the ability to exercise patience.Sometimes, the coach may decide to bench you and put in another player. Instead of throwing a fete, you should try and see matters from the coach&#39;s point of view, and try to learn from the player that replaced you.When you exercise patience, you&#39;re able to see matters from a different perspective, and if you can learn from that, then you have got a bright future waiting ahead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the actionable skills that you need to improve on in the field include;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>i. Spatial skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ii. Passing accuracy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iii. Dribbling skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iv. Body control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>v. Tactical knowhow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>12. The important take away.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clearly, there&#39;s a lot that goes into making a professionally recognized footballer. More even for those who want to have the successes and skillset that matches the great legends of football. The above skills and tactics should help you to dribble past the horde of footballers. Who knows, you just might have the nations chanting your name at the World Cup, it doesn&#39;t get better than that. Good luck.</p>','','pics/tips-skills-become-successful-football-player_ErmjiRe.jpg','2021-03-09 06:38:55.298007','2021-03-09 06:38:55.298079','2021-03-11 19:12:01.464450','rejected',685,25,0,0,'unlimited','Grammatical and spelling errors in the content. Article does not provide useful information.',0,0),(102,'4 Things You Need To Know About Becoming A Minimalist','4-things-you-need-to-know-about-becoming-a-minimalist','<p>Individuals around the world have a specific lifestyle that suits them and they are comfortable with the way things move around them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"a minimalist home setup\" height=\"928\" src=\"/media/post_images/Goldy/2021/03/09/img_20210309_163958.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Who is a Minimalist?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a set of individuals who believe in living well, having the best cars, living in the best apartment, having the latest technology at their disposal, and a whole lot of things.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the other hand, others don&#39;t fancy this type of lifestyle but prefer simpler things, necessity per se.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They don&#39;t engage in wasteful spending and only spend on their bills. Lots of things will come to mind, does it mean that I can&#39;t live the best life just because I want to save, or can&#39;t I just have anything I want?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This set of individuals are known as minimalists. You might wonder, does this word really exist?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"a minimalist living room\" height=\"366\" src=\"/media/post_images/Goldy/2021/03/09/img_20210309_164008.jpg\" width=\"720\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sure, it does. Minimalism is a word that means <strong>&quot;living with less&quot;</strong>. Minimalists are individuals who only pay for the essential things they need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They get rid of extravagance and luxury. They lead simple lives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They do not fall into the group who want the latest fashion of everything life has to offer. You might wonder if this set of people choose to suffer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A description of these types of people in detail is given below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A simple look at this definition might get some wondering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How can I become a minimalist?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are they any types of minimalists in the world?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Does it have advantages?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are there any side effects?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A look at these questions gives insight and understanding of the whole concept as a whole.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>(1) How do I become a minimalist?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Becoming a minimalist is not a day job. It takes discipline and self-denial to achieve this. The journey of becoming a minimalist is totally optional and the decision that takes a lot to make a reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This is how you can become a minimalist;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>&nbsp;Focus on the most important things: </strong>Some individuals find it difficult to stay put on a particular project. They are easily swayed by distractions and side talk. To achieve this effect, there is a need to get rid of anything that may cause distractions of any kind.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Do away with anything that doesn&#39;t make you glad:</strong> People around the world are mostly occupied with things that snatch their joy and keeps them in chains. The journey of minimalism requires you do away with them.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>&nbsp;You should be intentional about your aim:</strong> This is where the real job is. One cannot achieve an aim if one is not resilient about it. You might believe that challenges are for everyone, but when you keep up and choose not to relent.&nbsp;The achievement is always close.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>(2) Are there types of minimalists around the world?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The simple answer is&quot;yes&quot;. There is a long list but a few will be discussed.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>&nbsp;Essential minimalists:</strong> These are a set of individuals who are strict when it comes to spending. They only get the things they need and others are luxury.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Nomad minimalists:</strong> Nomads are initially known as people who live free lives. They have simple needs and have no concern with worldly problems. A good example of this&nbsp;group&nbsp;of people is&nbsp;monks. A nomadic minimalist is always ready to travel hence used to moving from place to place.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Frugal minimalists:</strong> Lots of individuals fall into this category. They spend a little amount of money strictly on necessities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This description might cast your mind to that person who hardly helps you when you are financially unstable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These groups of minimalists are usually not intentional.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>(3) Does being a minimalist have&nbsp;any advantage?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This is a good question. Which concept does not have advantages? Of course, it has. They are listed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>It saves time: The time that would have been spent on handling a whole lot of activities would be conserved, which improve efficiency.</li>\r\n	<li>It helps you focus on priorities: The more important things are handled and met in time. The choice to adopt minimalist behavior helps to face the most important things.</li>\r\n	<li>It improves productivity and focus: This applies to meeting up with a certain deadline. You may have a lot on your hands at the time. A minimalist stands to enjoy better productivity and more results.</li>\r\n	<li>It encourages conservation: This is the best part. You get to save more to handle issues that may concern your well-being, such as saving enough cash to handle a better project in the future.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>(4) Are there any side effects of being a minimalist?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Is there anything thing with the advantage that does not have disadvantages? The choice to become a minimalist is totally a choice but when it comes to investing in new things, it is usually a problem. A minimalist may have problems settling issues that do not concern them. This might bring personality clashes or problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The choice of the type of life to live is a matter of what appeals to you.</p>','#lifestyle #minimalist','pics/IMG_20210309_163958.jpg','2021-03-09 17:03:15.135205','2021-03-09 17:03:15.135258','2021-03-11 19:08:16.079150','published',669,21,1,1,'unlimited','Your article violates publishing guildlines',0,1);
